· Direct entry by applicants during the AHTF application process 
· Ongoing updates submitted by grantees as projects progress 
· Data entry and verification by AHTF staff as part of project management and compliance monitoring', 'Data is used to help inform budgeting/fiscal forecasting, to assess program effectiveness, and communicate the return on City investment to stakeholders, leadership, and the public.', NULL, 'Proxy isn’t necessary; Neighborly system + internal project management processes provide valid and consistent method for capturing data.', 'N/A', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
    (179, 'AGC3100', 4, 'Total affordable homeownership units created', 'Outcome', 'This measure captures the number of affordable housing units supported by AHTF investments during the reporting period. Units are counted once an applicant receives and accepts an AHTF award.', 'Data is sourced from the Neighborly application and data management system. Funding information is collected directly from applicants and grantees during the application process and updated throughout project development. Data is supplemented and validat', 'Kelvin Appiah / Wendi Redfern', 'Program Analyst / DC', 'Data is available on a rolling basis and updated continuously as projects progress. For reporting purposes, data is reviewed and finalized quarterly.', 'Development Division', 'Increase', NULL, NULL, 'Count', NULL, 'N/A', false, NULL, 'Neighborly application and data management system', 'Data is collected via: · Direct entry by applicants during the AHTF application process · Ongoing updates submitted by grantees as projects progress · Data entry and verification by AHTF staff as part of project management andcompliance monitoring', 'Data is used to help inform budgeting/fiscal forecasting, to assess program effectiveness, and communicate the return on City investment to stakeholders, leadership, and the public.', NULL, 'Proxy isn’t necessary; Neighborly system + internal project management processes provide valid and consistent method for capturing data.', 'Provide clear definitions of when a unit is considered "created."', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
    (180, 'AGC3100', 4, 'Total affordable rental housing units created', 'Outcome', 'This measure captures the number of affordable housing units supported by AHTF investments during the reporting period. Units are counted once an applicant receives and accepts an AHTF award.', 'Data is sourced from the Neighborly application and data management system. Funding information is collected directly from applicants and grantees during the application process and updated throughout project development. Data is supplemented and validate', 'Kelvin Appiah / Wendi Redfern', 'Program Analyst / DC', 'Data is available on a rolling basis and updated continuously as projects progress. For reporting purposes, data is reviewed and finalized quarterly.', 'Development Division', 'Increase', NULL, NULL, 'Count', NULL, 'N/A', false, NULL, 'Neighborly application and data management system', 'Data is collected via: · Direct entry by applicants during the AHTF application process · Ongoing updates submitted by grantees as projects progress · Data entry and verification by AHTF staff as part of project management andcompliance monitoring', 'Data is used to help inform budgeting/fiscal forecasting, to assess program effectiveness, and communicate the return on City investment to stakeholders, leadership, and the public.', NULL, 'Proxy isn’t necessary; Neighborly system + internal project management processes provide valid and consistent method for capturing data.', 'Provide clear definitions of when a unit is considered "created."', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
