    (330, 'AGC4356', 4, '# of K-12 schoolchildren, post-secondary students, and teachers served through BMA Educational Programs', 'Output', 'Participation by K-12 students, post-secondary students, and teachers in tours and programs', 'The BMA''s Education Department tracks participation for student and teacher programs in Airtable. Participation data is tracked in Google Analytics.', 'Doug Levering', 'Director of Grants & Sponsorship', 'Weekly', '15/100', 'Increase', NULL, NULL, 'Count', NULL, 'N/A', true, NULL, 'BMA servers; Google Analytics', 'The BMA''s Education Department tracks participation numbers for all student and teacher programs, records schools and the number of participating students and teachers through Airtable and compiles statistical data into a year-end report. For online programs, Google Analytics is utilized by Marketing and Visitor Experience staff to quantify participant data.', 'The BMA seeks to cultivate cultural understanding among young people and educators through the visual arts. Participation data is a key measurement of the BMA''s reach.', NULL, 'N/A', 'Identify the speciifc process and locations within the Airtable for pulling the data.', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
    (331, 'AGC4356', 4, 'Annual Attendance', 'Output', 'Visitation to the BMA''s facilities', 'Daily attendance tracked in an Airtable document.', 'Doug Levering', 'Director of Grants & Sponsorship', 'Daily', '27/100', 'Increase', NULL, NULL, 'Count', NULL, 'N/a', true, NULL, 'Airtable', 'BMA Visitor Services personel collect and record attendance figures at the East Lobby entrance.', 'Actual attendance, reflecting all onsite visitors to the BMA and its satellite location, directly effects earned revenue and impacts advertising and marketing decisions.', NULL, 'N/A', 'Identify the speciifc process and locations within the Airtable for pulling the data /', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
    (332, 'AGC4356', 4, 'Visibility value (# of impressions is a proxy measure for awareness of BMA as a cultural destination)', 'Output', 'Media impressions', 'Compilation of data from Muck Rack Software, radio broadcasters listener statistics, HYPESTAT online unique visitors to websites.', 'Doug Levering', 'Director of Grants & Sponsorship', 'Live', '30/100', 'Increase', NULL, NULL, 'Count', NULL, 'It''s suggested that the # of impressions is a proxy measure, so I''m curious if there is a formula you use to establish a "Visibility Value," or is Visibility Value just equal to the # of impressions.', false, NULL, 'BMA servers', 'CISION PR Software: provides circulation information of both digital (online) and print media (magazines and newspaper) which the BMA advertises with or appears in; Google Analytics: provides the visitor data to the BMA Press Room webpage, including unique visitors, sessions, page views, and time on site; Radio and television broadcast stations: provides estimated listener base numbers for the programming which the BMA advertises or participates in.', 'Media impressions are used as a proxy for visibility. Higher visibility helps attract visitors.', NULL, 'N/A', 'Identify the speciifc process and locations within the BMA servers for pulling the data.', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, true, true, 'Validated', '2026-06-01', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.816075'),
