    (1196, 13, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12000, 'Newly purchased digital equipment aided in efficiencies.', 14000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1197, 14, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6, NULL, 3, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1198, 15, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 35201, 'Off cycle checks include: bonus payments, sick leave conversion, election worker payments, termination payments, as well as on demand payments to correct a payroll shortage. During FY24, the volume of off-cycle checks required in response to payroll underpayments to employees continued to decline due to well planned bargaining unit MOU implementations, as well as improvement in end-user use of time and absence reporting.', 2200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1199, 16, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 385328, 'Payroll output is a direct relationship to the City''s vacancy/employment rate.', 360000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1200, 17, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.99, 'Through the implementation of direct deposit self-service in Workday, as well as the education efforts of both central payroll and Agency payroll/HR partners employees have been educated about the significant benefits of direct deposit enrollment.', 0.99, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1201, 18, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6, 'The ability to close the period timely during FY24 was most commonly impacted by system integration challenges.  Additional time was needed to address instances in which daily financial and accounting data from input systems (ex: UMAX, Mainframe, MUNIS) did not properly integrate and post to the City''s main system of record, Workday.', 5, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1202, 19, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 26, 'FY ''24 saw an increase of 4.7% in new claims and an increase of 15.2% in indemnity claims. BCPSS, DPW, and BCFD lead the increase with .09% (699), 34.6% (455), and 3.3% (443), respectively. DPW and BCFD also saw an increase in the incurred cost of 1.2% (16,284) and 11.6% (33,561).  The leading claims were: Striking against & stepping 76.4% (568), slips and falls 20.1% (542).  Motor vehicle accidents increased to 19.2% however the severity decreased.', 15, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1203, 20, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 776, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1204, 21, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4515, 'The projected number remains static at 2500; however, we tend to see an increase in testing based on the new hires or seasoned employees who now have driving privileges. There aren''t additional factors.', 3500, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1205, 22, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3350, NULL, 2715, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1206, 23, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 147, 'This is a new metric established for the Fiscal 2026 budget.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1207, 24, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'This is a new metric established as part of the Fiscal 2026 budget.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1208, 25, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.02, 'The Fiscal 2024 Budget was conservatively built to account for the continued gradual recovery after the COVID years. However, better than expected overall economic conditions helped us to yield unanticipated proceeds explaining the additional proceeds. The City experienced major budget surpluses from Income tax, returns on cash investments, property taxes, Highway User revenues, Recordation, Transfer, and Admission and Amusement taxes.', 0.02, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1209, 26, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4, 'This is a new metric proposed as part of the FY26 budget submission. The FY24 actual data is based on information from BOE Submit. FY24 was the first full fiscal year of utilizing BOE Submit for BOE materials. During FY24 BBMR also experienced significant turnover with Budget Analysts, turnover represents the greatest challenge in this process, as new analysts are less familiar with the context of the contractual information entered into the system and often require more time to review. This coincided with the learning curve across the organization as all users acclimated to the new system and new procedures.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1210, 27, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 305, 'The FY2024 actual number of CHAP appraisal reviews reflects 19% fewer CHAP appraisal reviews than what had been projected. This is attributed to fewer applications for the CHAP Tax Credit and is related to the uncertain economic environment and rising mortgage interest rates.', 377, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1211, 28, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 783, 'New Performance Measure.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1212, 29, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 167, 'Over time, applicants have become more familiar with the specific requirements needed to be eligible for or to maintain eligibility for credits. As a result, fewer applications are being rejected or revoked than initially projected.', 285, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1213, 30, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9016000, 'The estimate of the Actual Increase in Property Tax Revenue Attributable to Successful Appeals has increased significantly as the appeals that were ultimately filed included much greater increases in residential and multi-family property values than originally estimated. These increased values are a result of the increased demand that occurred following the pandemic and the increased activity that occurred in advance of increasing interest rates.', 2920000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1214, 31, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3847, 'Our projection for the number of tax credit applications granted for FY2024 overestimated the number of credits that would be awarded for the Energy Conservation Devices tax credit, resulting in a shortfall in the actual number granted.', 3975, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1215, 39, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.06, 'The Fiscal 2024 actual data was impacted by the Federal Reserve holding interest rates at a high level to combat inflation.  The Federal Reserve did not begin cutting interest rates until the beginning of Fiscal 2025, which did not impact Fiscal 2024.', 0.05, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1216, 40, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.01, 'The increased use of data collected through company level inspections to identify patterns and identify areas at higher risk of multiple alarm fires.', 0, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1217, 41, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8975, 'Increased reinforcement of units activating the proper status within their Mobile Data Terminals and continued use of AVL dispatch procedures.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1218, 42, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2.56, 'Increase in the number of fires in occupied dwellings and the underutilization of BCFD’s smoke detector program.', 0, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1219, 43, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 18214, 'The establishment and continued use of Target Enforcement Zones (TEZ) for selected areas which increased the number of days inspections are performed each week. Expanded use of data source material has led to enhanced focus within areas determined to be of higher risk for in-home fires.', 12000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1220, 44, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 25, 'After the COVID pandemic, the CERT program was in recovery mode. In FY24, OEM was able to revitalize the CERT program, engaging local leaders to participate. The community has lost familiarity with the program, so it has taken a lot of effort with community outreach to inform and rebuild.', 15, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1221, 45, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, 'We hired a training and exercise coordinator in 2024, and we continued to strengthen relationships with our partner agencies by addressing some of their training needs.', 5, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1222, 46, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 55, 'The actual 2024 on-scene response was dependent on the number of large-scale, inter-agency emergencies in the city. _x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 35, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1223, 47, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'We will continue to develop the training and exercise program. With available staff and ongoing interagency and public-private partnerships, our training capabilities will be able to double from FY24 to FY26. Additionally, we will be developing a training and exercise plan with input from our partners to better serve the needs of staff citywide.', 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1224, 48, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 161814, 'Continuing to work on innovative programs to reduce overutilization of 911 for low acuity responses.', 160000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1225, 49, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9433, 'This is a new program and the number f outreached patients exceeded our expectations.', 1200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1226, 50, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5138, 'Working to improve response time to be in compliance with NFPA. Reasons for not meeting the goals include high call volume, delay in hospital offload, and lack of available units.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1227, 51, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '100 % of ePCR reports are reviewed by QA through the First Pass System.', 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1228, 52, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.262, 'There was a marked improvement in the cardiac arrest survivor rate from FY 22-FY 23, with an improvement from 22% in 2022 to 27% in 2023. One major factor in this improvement is due to the addition of the LUCAS device, which is a mechanical CPR device.                                                        The 35% rate is a national goal. There are several reasons for the inability to reach the goal such as access to defibrillators, public awareness and education, bystander intervention and community health factors.', 0.42, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1229, 53, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2989, 'Several factors influenced the performance metric for the number of citizens trained in hands-only CPR including the following:_x000D_
_x000D_
•	Community Outreach Efforts: The availability and frequency of public training sessions, workshops, or events directly impact how many individuals are trained._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Public Awareness Campaigns: Effective promotion and education about the importance of hands-only CPR can drive greater participation._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Funding and Resources: Adequate funding for training materials, staffing, and venues supports larger and more frequent sessions._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Accessibility: Offering training in diverse locations, at various times, and with minimal cost or barriers encourages higher turnout._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Partnerships and Support: Collaborations with schools, businesses, and community organizations expand outreach and participation._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Social and Cultural Factors: Public interest, trust in emergency services, and cultural attitudes toward health training can influence participation rates._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Tracking and Reporting: Accurate measurement and follow-up efforts to identify gaps or successful strategies also play a role in improving this metric._x000D_
_x000D_', 7500, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1230, 54, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, 25, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1231, 55, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9324, 'Several factors influenced the performance metric for the number of leave-behind naloxone kits distributed to the public including the following:_x000D_
_x000D_
•	Overdose Rates: Higher rates of opioid overdoses increase the opportunity and need for naloxone distribution by EMS providers._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Availability of Kits: Adequate supply and funding for purchasing naloxone kits directly impact the number available for distribution._x000D_
_x000D_
•	EMS Protocols: Policies that allow or encourage EMS providers to distribute kits during overdose responses affect distribution metrics._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Community Awareness: Public knowledge and acceptance of naloxone as a life-saving tool can influence whether individuals are willing to receive and use the kits._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Training and Education: EMS providers and community members who are well-educated on naloxone use are more likely to participate in distribution efforts._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Collaboration with Organizations: Partnerships with health departments, nonprofits, and harm reduction groups can expand the scope of distribution._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Data Collection and Targeting: Identifying high-risk areas and targeting those communities ensures naloxone distribution efforts are focused where they are needed most._x000D_
_x000D_
•	Legal and Policy Environment: Local or state laws and guidelines regarding naloxone use and distribution impact how widely it can be distributed._x000D_
_x000D_', 5000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1232, 56, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 85, NULL, 75, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1233, 57, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 304, 'The number of fire and life safety presentation requests made by the public can be influenced by several factors.  One of the factors that impacted community presentation requests was a lack of awareness about the availability and benefits of such programs. Another factor was perception, some citizens perceive fire and life safety presentations as irrelevant to their personal circumstances.', 278, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1234, 58, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 18310, 'Economic follow of the City''s needs increased and more personal increased the numbers.', 14000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1235, 59, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2270, 'The number of use and occupancy permits issued is primarily driven by customer demand, as these permits are essential for businesses and property owners to legally operate within local zoning and safety requirements. However, the process can be impacted by staffing levels within the Office of the Fire Marshal. The staffing challenge can lead to longer wait times for inspection approvals, affecting the efficiency of the inspection process.', 2000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1236, 60, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1260, 'The process was impacted by staffing levels within the Office of the Fire Marshal. The staffing challenge can lead to longer wait times for inspection approvals, affecting the efficiency of the inspection process.', 2400, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (2786, 61, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'The FY27 target reflects continued emphasis on training compliance. Leadership has reinforced expectations to ensure investigators maintain required certifications and remain current on investigative practices.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1238, 62, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.87, 'No dedicated members to address complaints', 0.8, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1239, 63, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The number of plans review requested is driven by customer demand, as these permits are essential for businesses and property owners to legally operate within local zoning and safety requirements. However, the process can be impacted by staffing levels within the Office of the Fire Marshal. The staffing challenge can lead to longer wait times for inspection approvals, affecting the efficiency of the inspection process.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1240, 64, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 95, 'Fire investigators try to determine how fires begin by applying the scientific method. Through observation and measurement, they can formulate a hypothesis, test it and form a conclusion about the fire’s origin and cause._x000D_
_x000D_
Since there is limited time to collect witness accounts and details upon arriving at an emergency scene, fire investigators must follow a process. This may include:_x000D_
_x000D_
Evaluating the scene_x000D_
_x000D_
Documenting the scene by taking notes and photographs_x000D_
_x000D_
Collecting and processing evidence_x000D_
_x000D_
Interviewing witnesses _x000D_
_x000D_
Having all of the afore mentioned factors align leads to successful cause determination. Not having same is a directly contributes to cause being listed as "undetermined".', 90, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1241, 65, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 497, 'Incidents where fire investigation services are needed vary by call type and are not easily predicted. Investigations can occur at the "unit" level, where the company officer is able to determine cause and origin without having to request an investigator. Other incidents involving suspicion of arson or where the cause of the fire are unclear, necessitate an investigator. 2024 data is based upon the initial "undetermined" status of a fire scene.', 500, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1242, 66, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'The BCFD has revised policy that drives when/where personnel are permitted to enter a structure. As such, structures determined to be in unsafe condition (Code X) are not entered for cause determination purposes. This new policy can drive down the number of structure fires where cause determination is needed.', 0.95, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1243, 67, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'The percentage of closed fire investigations can be affected by various factors including weather, building stability, the collection and preservation of evidence and significant fire damage.', 0.5, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1244, 68, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.66, 'Determining the cause of a fire is complex, often impacted by several factors. A primary obstacle is the extent of damage caused by the fire itself, which can adulterate key evidence needed to determine the fire''s origin. The presence of multiple ignition sources can also complicate the investigative process. In locations with electrical devices or flammable materials, pinpointing the exact cause becomes particularly challenging. Environmental conditions at the time of the fire, such as wind, humidity, and temperature, influence how a fire spreads and behaves, adding complexity to determining its origin and cause. These conditions can alter the fire''s dynamics complicating the overall investigative process.', 0.6, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1245, 69, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'The factors that impact this goal involve funding and member’s being on duty to receive the training courses.', 0.75, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1246, 70, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'There was no impact to this metric to prevent target goal achievement.', 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1247, 71, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.92, 'Total compliance of all gear was not achieved due to members being off duty injured and sick. As such, members'' turnout gear was inaccessible at the time at which it was due for repair/replacement.', 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1248, 72, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, 'There was no impact to this metric as the goal was met and proceeding as planned for implementation.', 7, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
