    (1350, 186, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 147, 'This is a newly proposed metric.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1351, 187, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 288, 'The Office of Rehabilitation Services was able to surpass the original goal of 200 houses served', 200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1352, 188, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'The fiscal year 24 data was impacted by the decrease in Project CORE work and challenges in establishing a new demolition contract.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1353, 189, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 73261, 'Inspections completed is market driven and tied to the number of permits issued, the complexity of the work (inspections required) and the need for repeat inspections. Increased enforcement and continued education around permitting and inspections also leads to additional inspections being scheduled.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1354, 190, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'Completion of inspections on the date scheduled is a key customer service indicator. Staff availability and flexibility has allowed us to achieve a 98% on time completion rate.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1355, 191, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 41923, 'The total number of permits issued is a measure of the overall state of investment in the City, reflecting the strength of the economy and the desirability of city living.', 38940, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1356, 192, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 13366, 'A renewed focus on reducing the number of vacant buildings in Baltimore. A decline in vacants has been a combination of public and private efforts. DHCD has expanded the use of In Rem foreclosure, streamlined the disposition process while continuing to deploy strategic code enforcement (receivership) and demolition. At the same time the private market is continuing to complete rehabilitations of vacant buildings.', 13199, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1357, 193, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 450, 'This is a new performance measure selected for FY26 to reflect the service changes made to SRV752.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1358, 195, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1181, 'This is a new performance measure selected for FY26 to reflect the service changes made to SRV752.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1359, 196, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 522178, 'The Summer Food Program provided 429,827 meals served. This was impacted by not reaching a goal of 300 sites to provide meals.', 600000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1360, 197, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 239, 'SFS sites were not able to recruit enough new sites to reach our goals', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1361, 198, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.09, 'We were able to reduce the unused meals count down from 10% to 9%', 0.04, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1362, 204, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'Agency staff were required to participate in mandatory training for the roll out of performance management in Workday contributing to a higher completion rate. This was coupled with consistent and ongoing outreach by the Office of Learning and Development when people enroll in courses. Additionally, agencies are seeing the benefit of allowing their employees time to complete trainings and working with the Office of Learning and Development to identify training needs for targeted trainings for their employees.', 0.7, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1363, 207, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.05, 'The Fiscal 2024 actual is lower than the target because it was only the second year of the program and DHR did not have a baseline for participation when the FY 2024 target was established. DHR does not have the authority to mandate that supervisors participate in leadership training and must engage in outreach with agencies to encourage them to have their people leaders participate. This resulted in a lower actual than what was targeted.', 0.15, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1364, 209, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.594, 'During Fiscal 2024, DHR began engaging with each of the health care vendors to increase the number of offerings to city employees around wellness. Additionally, DHR held its first in-person wellness fair since the start of the Covid-19 pandemic.', 0.25, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1365, 210, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.93, 'Previous years included all the courses or just new employee orientation. FY 2024 is the first year that we have the most collective and full year of participant ratings on content created internally. Any of the courses designed internally by Learning and Development follow ADDIE design principles.', 0.8, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1366, 211, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'EAP had 578 cases opened between 7/1/23 and 6/30/24. The four clinicians see each client on average between 4 to 6 times. Substance abuse clients stay with EAP for a full year, and they have monthly sessions. EAP works diligently with clients to resolve cases and limit returns due to the same initial intake reason.', 0.97, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1367, 212, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.0577, 'Retirees have only been able to enroll in Workday for open enrollment over the last two years. Many retirees are familiar with the paper-based forms and prefer to complete their open enrollment that way. DHR has seen a small increase from the first year of tracking data from 5% to 6% and anticipates the percentage growing over time.', 0.2, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1368, 213, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.905, 'Compared to FY 2023, the Office of Classification and Compensation had more large-scale projects which take significantly longer for analysts to complete. An increase in these large-scale projects also impact the speed with which analysts can complete their other projects, reducing the % completed on time from the prior year. The Office did meet its Fiscal 2024 performance target.', 0.85, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1369, 214, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 29207, 'Numbers for Fiscal 2024 continue to be higher than the target due to the continued roll out of Performance Management in Workday. Employees were required to take several trainings around the rollout leading to the increased numbers.', 8000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1370, 215, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2147, 'DHR continues to see high project requests coming into the Office of Classification and Compensation, specifically around salary. 17% of all projects submitted during Fiscal 2024 were In-Range Adjustments. This is second only to Reclassifications (17.6% of total projects). Agencies are submitting these projects to retain staff and remain competitive with outside entities.', 1000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1371, 216, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 190, 'The actual data for FY24 for this performance metric was impacted by external factors including the increased use of scooters and bicycles in the rights of way, the accelerating deterioration of the City’s infrastructure (with resulting sewer backups), and the collapse of vacant houses, which resulted in the increased number of lawsuits received.', 200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1372, 217, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'Internal factors impacted the FY24 actual data for this performance metric.  Internal factors included (a) continued improvement of standard operational procedures for claim response times (b) aggressive personnel actions (recruitment and competitive competition) to ensure the CBI team was appropriately staffed to accommodate response time and (c)  drafting of claim response templates to expedite the response time.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1373, 218, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.15, 'Factors that impacted this performance metrics actual data in FY24 include the ability of the Labor & Employment team to (a) have familiarity with agency operational structure and agency needs; (b) familiarity with the laws and policies that impact City agencies and employment; and (c) clear and concise advice of counsel._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 0.05, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1374, 219, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'The factors that impacted the FY24 actual data for this performance metric centered on the efforts to fully staff the Advice & Opinions team with trained and knowledgeable attorneys that can handle high volumes for requests and manage emergency (last minute) requests as well.  The A&O team also worked with their clients to identify and forecast upcoming legislation and bills to be prepared to provide legal advice and opinions in a timely manner.  Finally, internal SOP''s were updated to prioritize legislation and bill report response times.', 0.95, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1375, 220, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Factors that impacted the FY24 actual data for the performance metric include number of survey participants (down by 5% from previous survey years) and the ability of the practice groups response times as well legal advice/counsel that was provided.', 0.95, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1376, 221, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 417, 'External and internal factors impacted the FY24 actual data for this performance metric.  Ensuring that police misconduct is exposed – and appropriate discipline meted out when necessary – is the best way to improve the overall trust between the community and BPD.  Legal Affairs’ work with PIB is also required by the Consent Decree, and the relationship between these offices is key to advancing these goals.  Legal Affairs’ attorneys must be flexible and adapt to different priorities in the area of police discipline, and often must navigate the complicated relationship between the FOP, officers themselves, and BPD management.  As such, Legal Affairs’ attorneys must maintain an excellent working and professional relationship with legal counsel for FOP, and have continued to grow this bond over the past year.  As a result, Legal Affairs is increasingly successful in resolving disciplinary matters without the need for an administrative hearing.  Instead, Legal Affairs quite often effectively manages the caseload through a variety of means, sometimes negotiating settlements, convincing members to resign in lieu of termination, and otherwise striving to discipline/remove problematic BPD employees.', 200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1377, 222, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.96, 'The use of dispositive motions impacted the FY24 actual data for this performance metric.  Dispositive motions argue that that the case should be dismissed as a matter of law.  This aggressive strategy has been met with great success, as Courts have granted – at least in part – almost all of the briefs filed by Legal Affairs.  This has the important practical effect of winnowing a given case down to core issues, while also affirmatively demonstrating to plaintiffs that BPD will vigorously defend all cases brought against it.  Another metric for success is the mediation/settlement of cases well below the initial demand asked by plaintiffs.  Legal Affairs’ attorneys have been extraordinarily successful in tenaciously negotiating settlements at values far below market-rates.  By assessing liability and leveraging the best legal arguments available, Legal Affairs’ attorneys have consistently saved the Baltimore City taxpayers millions each year through their efforts.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
    (1378, 223, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 68, NULL, 100, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
