    (1398, 247, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'The Mayor’s Office of LGBTQ Affairs experienced several factors that impacted our fiscal year 2024 metrics:_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Audited Forms:_x000D_
_x000D_
While our target was to audit six agencies, we were only able to audit two. This shortfall occurred because, starting in January 2024, the office transitioned to being a single-person operation, requiring me to manage audits independently with only six months remaining in the fiscal year. Additionally, some agencies did not respond promptly, delaying the audit process._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Single-Stall Restrooms:_x000D_
_x000D_
We exceeded our target of three single-stall restrooms with six completed audits, achieving 100% over our margin—a significant success despite limited resources._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Social Media Followers:_x000D_
_x000D_
Our goal of 4,000 followers fell short at 271 due to the need to establish entirely new accounts after the previous director refused to relinquish login credentials. This challenge significantly hindered our ability to rebuild an audience within the fiscal year._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Attended Events:_x000D_
_x000D_
We attended 16 events, almost doubling our target and reflecting the office’s proactive engagement with the community despite staffing constraints._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Training Public Safety Officers:_x000D_
_x000D_
Although our training numbers were 50 officers, we are optimistic about future growth due to new partnerships with the Fire Department and EMT divisions, which will expand our training capacity citywide._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Sponsored Events:_x000D_
_x000D_
The office sponsored seven events, nearly doubling our target and demonstrating our commitment to visibility and community engagement._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Event Attendance:_x000D_
_x000D_
Our average attendance across events was 15,200, indicating strong community interest and participation in our programs._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Despite resource challenges, these metrics underscore the office’s resilience, strategic adaptation, and commitment to advancing LGBTQ equity and inclusion in Baltimore.', 6, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
