    (1427, 306, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20.5, 'While this number is lower than FY23, it represents our optimized approach to tracking our CIAA media coverage. This year we''ve excluded tracking of the more blanket "CIAA + Baltimore" keyword and placed more emphasis on high-quality results. We will use this tracking approach going forward. We also spent more time this year cultivating our content creator/influencer strategy, which shifted some of our from traditional media, resulting in high but lower than the previous year''s results.', 30, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.997112'),
