    (1535, 445, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.76, 'Failure to submit a "benchmark" OID on time results in an instant failure (a 0). When you remove those from the calculation, the actual average is 94%. The lowest score on any 1 benchmark test in the evaluation period was 78%. This means, that in general, benchmarks largely improved and that the ''score'' only appears the same due to the ''missed'' submissions of certain benchmarks that dragged down the overall averages.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1536, 446, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'We exceeded the goal of having 90% on our Procedural Justice score cards.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1537, 447, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.97, 'The Warrant Apprehension Task Force (WATF) served 74 homicide warrants in 2024, resulting in a 93.24% clearance rate.  Approximately five 2024 open warrants were carried into 2025, commonly due to the criminal element continuously using tactics to evade and elude capture by law enforcement.  This includes but is not limited to fleeing outside of jurisdiction, state boundaries, and countries and obtaining new addresses, electronics, and identification.  This methodology hinders the time and capture of suspects, resulting in a lapse before arrest.', 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1538, 448, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.17, 'Physical agility changes in place 6/1 - stricter requirements prior.', 0.15, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1539, 449, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.63, 'Targeted marketing', 0.3, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1540, 450, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 178, 'The increase in the number of High Risk Warrant services for the FY24 goal was due to more request for High Risk Warrant service from investigations being conducted by other Units within the BPD and outside Agencies.', 125, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1541, 451, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 172, 'The on-scene fuming chamber has not been deployed.  It is currently in the quality assurance process and is expected to be in use by the end of FY25 Q1.  We have also begun crime scene documentation using drones and we''ve seen an uptick in this category.  We expect this particular service to expand rapidly in calendar year 2025.', 175, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1542, 452, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1181, 'The Special Operations Section Callouts exceded projections due to the increase of incidents requiring assistance from Special Operations Section Units. Example: Collapse of the Key Bridge.', 1000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1543, 453, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 115, 'Competitive Job Market_x000D_
_x000D_
Increased competition from other law enforcement agencies and industries offering higher pay, better benefits, or less physically demanding roles may have reduced interest in police recruitment._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Public Perception of Law Enforcement_x000D_
_x000D_
Negative perceptions of law enforcement, influenced by high-profile incidents and social movements, may have deterred potential candidates from pursuing a career in policing._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Stringent Hiring Standards_x000D_
_x000D_
High standards for applicants, including physical and psychological tests, background checks, and disqualification criteria, could have limited the pool of eligible recruits._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Challenging Physical Fitness Requirements_x000D_
_x000D_
The physical agility test may have been a barrier for some potential recruits, especially given its rigorous nature or perceived difficulty._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Economic Factors_x000D_
_x000D_
Economic uncertainty, including inflation and financial instability, may have led some individuals to prioritize more stable or financially rewarding careers outside of law enforcement._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Limited Recruitment Outreach_x000D_
_x000D_
Insufficient or ineffective recruitment marketing, outreach, and community engagement efforts could have failed to connect with diverse, qualified candidates, particularly within Baltimore City._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Internal Staffing Shortages_x000D_
_x000D_
A shortage of recruiters and limited resources for recruitment campaigns could have led to a reduced ability to effectively reach and engage potential recruits.', 200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
