    (1548, 458, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7070, 'One large driver of the increase was the training needed in order to stand up the new Digital Forensics Unit.  Nearly 2000 of the total number of training hours were as a result of bringing this service online and new hires in the unit.  Another driver of the increase was the use of grant funding to support some additional training in other units. And finally, the widespread availability of local and online training has increased our ability to deliver more forensic, quality assurance, and leadership content to our scientists.', 6500, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
