    (1595, 505, 2024, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.825, 'Several factors impacted the FY2024 aquatics data, including facility closures. Druid Hill Pool was closed for AFRAM and experienced multiple closures due to sewage issues. O''Donnell Heights remained closed for a significant portion of the summer, while William McAbee faced repeated closures due to vandalism.', 0.85, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
