    (1701, 18, 2025, 5.33, NULL, 5.33, NULL, 5.66, NULL, 6, 'In Q4, April and May were closed in 5 days. June closed took place in 8 days to allow extended time for agencies to process Year-end journal entries. This is standard practice at year end.', 6, 'FY25 results are slightly skewed because the year end close process extends the amount of days month end close for June of 2025.', 5, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
