    (1844, 171, 2025, 37037, NULL, 32350, NULL, 37212, NULL, 41705, NULL, 148683, 'This was a direct result of the attrition.  During this period, we experienced a staffing decrease due to individuals moving on to other opportunities, and workforce challenges in the hiring process.', 190000, 'The target is a combination of the re-inspection of open notices, 311 service requests and inspector-initiated request for action. We analyzed historical inspection data, while factoring in staffing variations, seasonal fluctuations, and special projects to  establish this target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1845, 172, 2025, 0.66, NULL, 0.74, NULL, 0.92, NULL, 0.96, NULL, 0.81, 'This was a direct result of the attrition.', 0.85, 'We analyzed historical SR data, while factoring in staffing variations, seasonal fluctuations, and special projects to establish this target.  Timely response to resident complaints is key to providing good customer service.  Experience tells us that there will always be some matters beyond our control that require an SR to go beyond the expected time to close.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1846, 173, 2025, 0.9995, NULL, 1, NULL, 0.96, NULL, 0.95, NULL, 0.97, 'Increased efficiency in operations due to the partnership between Special Operations and the Ombudsmen Team, and improved collaborations with BPD, BGE, DPW, the Mayors Office of Homeless Services, DPW-Water and HHP Crisis Response all contribute greatly to the success of our vacate operation.', 0.75, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1847, 174, 2025, 0, NULL, 1826, NULL, 1164, NULL, 1376, NULL, 1376, 'We have increased enforcement efforts during FY 26 along with additional pressure from the Courts in requiring license for certain eviction related cases.Transition to a new permit and licensing system likely impacted the number of contractors renewing licenses. Some contractors do not regularly do', 1800, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1848, 175, 2025, 33630, NULL, 38282, NULL, 32395, NULL, 33731, 'Property registration is based on the calendar year so Q1 and Q2 reflect the 2024 registration year and Q3 and Q4 represent the 2025 calendar year. The total properties registered at the end of Q4 would be the total proeprties registered for the FY. The total number for Q2 is the total number registered for the  prior registration year.', 33731, 'Enforcement efforts were increased over the past fiscal year but we did not see major gains in compliance with the code. We believe this may be due to economic factors related to increase costs.', 60000, 'Maintaining the same target as FY24 as we continue to improve owner compliance in registering their properties.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1849, 176, 2025, 0.58, NULL, 0.45, NULL, 0.65, NULL, 0.87, NULL, 0.87, 'We have increased enforcement efforts during FY 26 along with additional pressure from the Courts in requiring license for certain eviction related cases.', 0.7, 'Maintaining the same target as FY24 as we continue to improve owner compliance in licensing their properties.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
