    (1858, 185, 2025, 21, NULL, 17, NULL, 15, NULL, 15, 'One lead grant expired which also meant a reduction in contractors.  Lead currently going through the procurement process to add additional contractors shortly.', 68, '1 grant went into close out period while the new grant was in "ramp up phase", meaning more prep work and assessments than full house remediation.', 90, 'With the influx of the Healthy Home ARPA dollars, it should allow us to complete more cases', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
