    (1869, 197, 2025, 249, NULL, 249, NULL, 0, NULL, 143, 'The SFSP number of sites is down in the 4th quarter due to upgrading the web sites that caused a number of sites to experience issues with uploading their data.  The number of sites will increase for the 1st quarter by close to 50%.   _x000D_
