The program runs from June to August each year, and straddles fiscal years. The FY25 total is the total number of sites for the CY24 program.', 249, 'Number of sites impacted by conversion to new system and change in location', 210, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1870, 198, 2025, 0.09, NULL, 0.08, NULL, 0, NULL, 0.11, 'The increase in the number of unused meals in the 4th quarter was due to initial program set up and coordination with our partners in providing 48 hour advance cancellations notification of meals to us  prior to the scheduled delivery date.', 0.09, '% of meals unused was impacted by site locations and times open', 0.04, 'with enhance training for our sites we should able to reduce unused meals', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1871, 204, 2025, 0.82, NULL, 0.77, NULL, 0.69, NULL, 0.0105, 'There were 5,862 enrollments into virtual courses in Q4, however there were 6,129 completions in virtual courses. A percentage greater than 100% occurs when more employees completed virtual courses, in this time period than enrolled, which occurs because of the carryover enrollments that are now completed from the previous quarter.', 0.8, 'There were five (5) courses that had over 200 enrollments in a “not started” status, they include:  COMPLIANCE SHORT: Promoting Diversity and Avoiding Discrimination, Harassment Prevention for US Employees – Workplace v2.0, Language Access | Mayor’s Office of Immigrant Affairs (MIMA), (Course) Criti', 0.7, 'The target is established based on historical data, performance, and anticipated challenges. The adoption of Workday Learning provides great opportunity and ease for employees to enroll in courses, however, it’s effectiveness to increase completion remains unknown.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1872, 205, 2025, 81, NULL, 76, NULL, 66, NULL, 79, NULL, 75, 'Technical calls requires research. Prior history.', 30, 'This is a new target for the agency. We established the target based on what we believe is a realistic estimate for Benefits staff to answer calls based on their workload.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1873, 206, 2025, 12.95, NULL, 10.5, NULL, 10.16, NULL, 12.93, 'Data reflects the time between when an applicant submits their application for a position and when DHR refers the candidate to the agency (if they meet the minimum qualifications for the position).', 12, 'This is an established Service Level Agreement (SLA) for Civil Service Positions/Postings which require an eligibility list.', 15, 'DHR utilized the baseline of its review period for applications of 10 days that was established during a prior performance audit. However it is being raised to 15 days for Fiscal 2025 due to the proposed abolishment of 1 filled Recruitment and Talent Acquisition Specialist II.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1874, 207, 2025, 0.013, NULL, 0.012, NULL, 0.059, NULL, 0.014, NULL, 0.1, 'This metric should be revised, as it does not account for the decreasing denominator over time. As employees complete the program, they should be removed from the total population. Currently, the percentage trained shows little to no movement because new supervisors are continually added to the deno', 0.2, 'We do not yet have data for this target in prior years but we anticipate continued messaging of the program and engagement with agencies will increase participation.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1875, 208, 2025, 0.606, NULL, 0.609, NULL, 0.576, NULL, 0.639, NULL, 0.61, NULL, 0.6, 'Newly established target is based on current % of employees that are residents.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1876, 209, 2025, 0.3, NULL, 0.068, NULL, 0.065, NULL, 0.167, NULL, 0.6, 'Communication platforms, city-wide activities and incentives.', 0.25, 'The target is remaining consistent with Fiscal 2024. Target will be reevaluated as participation increases.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1877, 210, 2025, 0.97, NULL, 0.8, NULL, 0.91, NULL, 0.94, NULL, 0.88, 'There are four (4) courses that are primarily responsible for detractors and neutral scores and present an opportunity to update and redesign them to increase training satisfaction. Of these four (4) courses, two (2) are deployed in collaboration with partnering agencies.', 0.8, 'The target is set based on combining industry benchmarking for the Customer Satisfaction Score (CSAT), American Customer Satisfaction Index (ACSI), and American Productivity & Quality Center (APQC) within the training industry. Though benchmarking recognizes 74.4% as the US customer satisfaction score, due to the importance of education and training our target is increased. Overall, we have lowered the target due to historical data, and anticipated challenges. The target is a goal, and though it''s attainable under perfect conditions it''s a challenge due to unknown factors that may arise and our continued use of the same content.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1878, 211, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Data is caculated on an annual basis and cannot be reported quarterly. Clients are tracked across the entire fiscal year.', 0.9792, '1.	Effective short term, clinical interventions._x000D_
_x000D_
2.	Successful rapport building with clients._x000D_
_x000D_
3.	Client concerns are often situational and isolated events/circumstances that are resolved._x000D_
_x000D_
4.	Longer wait times to assessment._x000D_
_x000D_', 0.97, 'The target is based on historical data from the Employee Assistance Program (EAP) and industry standards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1879, 212, 2025, NULL, NULL, 0.0334, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Open Enrollment for benefits took place during Q2 of FY 2025. Data is only calculated in quarter that Open Enrollment takes place.', 0.03, 'City subsidies provided to retirees impacted the fiscal 2025 actual data.', 0.2, 'The target was established based on the number of retirees that are currently utilizing Workday for benefits. DHR is continuing to make concerted efforts to engage with the retiree population to continually increase the number of retirees using Workday for their benefits selections. Retirees that make their selections in Workday can automatically see their selections versus having to mail, fax or email them to the Office of Employee Benefits to have them entered into Workday.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1880, 213, 2025, 0.831, NULL, 0.849, NULL, 0.83, NULL, 0.904, NULL, 0.85, NULL, 0.875, 'We are raising this target slightly based on performance in prior years. However, we are only raising it by a modest level because we continue to face issues with vacancies within Class and Comp and see a significant increase in the number of requests from agencies. DHR believes requests will continue to increase unless prior and current large scale salary studies that have been conducted are implemented. DHR is also proposing to eliminate one C&C position to meet its budgetary target', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1881, 214, 2025, 12258, NULL, 7685, NULL, 11462, NULL, 6524, NULL, 37890, 'FY25 enrollments significantly exceeded target due to enterprise-wide initiatives and coordinated agency training plans, including BCFD’s quarterly enrollment strategy. This was further amplified by increased adoption of Workday Learning and strong collaboration between L&D and agencies to deliver s', 8000, 'The target  is set based on historical data trends, performance, anticipated improvement, and city-wide adoption to Workday Learning. The target is a goal, and though attainable under perfect conditions it’s still a challenge due to unknown factors that may arise. Targets are also generated with the assumption that access to packaged content remains, and projects_x000D_
_x000D_
stay on course.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1882, 215, 2025, 562, NULL, 535, NULL, 518, NULL, 408, 'Fiscal 2025 data includes projects that were submitted to the Office of Classification and Compensation beginning July 1, 2024.', 2023, NULL, 1000, 'We plan to hold our target consistent with our target in prior years as we do not anticipate a reduction in requests coming in from agencies.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1883, 216, 2025, 66, NULL, 56, NULL, 70, NULL, 65, NULL, 257, 'Volumes of claims filed against the City of Baltimore, public safety and policing incidents (within the fiscal year) and monitoring of major incidents or systemic events (i.e., neighborhood water main break).', 250, 'Resolution of cases within a short time frame decreases the amount of resources (and possible payout) for the City of Baltimore', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1884, 217, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 'Claim volume, staffing capacity (maintained at 100%), interagency coordination (improving request response times for incident reports and evidence availability), and istreamlining of internal processes by implementing a claims management system.', 0.98, 'Increase response time and improve communication with claimants', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1885, 218, 2025, 0.248, NULL, 0.257, NULL, 0, NULL, 0.297, NULL, 0.3, 'Factors that impacted the FY25 actual data include size and type of employment claims as well as the strength and expertise of the Labor & Employment legal defense which reduced amount paid in damages claimed as well as reduced further litigation and liability risk.', 0.016, 'Reduce payouts amounts through negotiation, settlements or winning of cases thus reducing the overall expended amount for the City', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1886, 219, 2025, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 'Volume of legislation introduced, complexity of proposed legislation and timing of legislative requests.  To maintain the 100% submisison rate, the Advice & Opinions team prioritize all bill review requests ane ensures staffing capacity to respond within requested deadlines.', 1, 'Ensures timely review and passing of critical legislation for the City', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1887, 220, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Data for this KPI is gathered via annual survey sent to service''s clients. Because of this, partial quarterly data is not available.', 1, 'Factors that impacted the FY25 actual data was the abillity of attorneys to establish and maintain working relationships with internal and external stakeholders.  The working relationships are rooted in timely communication, trust in expertise of attorneys and transparency in opinions/decisions.', 1, 'Ensures clients needs are being met in a timely and effective manner', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1888, 221, 2025, 83, NULL, 175, NULL, 99, NULL, 73, NULL, 430, 'Factors that impacted the FY25 actual data - 1) streamlining of internal review processes and oversight 2) improved coordination and collaboration with the Public Integrity Bureau', 240, 'Continued reduction in the backlog to ensure timely processing of misconduct cases in compliance with the federal consent decree and requirement of the Performance Review Board', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1889, 222, 2025, 0.61, NULL, 0.66, NULL, 0.7, NULL, 0.1, NULL, 0.1197, 'There are a number of factors that impacted the FY25 actual data including consent decree requirements, union/contractual protections and quality/clarity of presented evidence (strong evidence often encourages officers to accepted negotiated discipline versus hearings)', 0.95, 'To achieve significant progress on implementation and compliance of the federal consent decree, focused on policing practices and holding officers accountable.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1890, 223, 2025, 12, NULL, 16, NULL, 10, NULL, 7, NULL, 45, 'The number of appeals handled indicates our abillity to handle and win claims (for Baltimore City) before the Workers Compensation Commission, indicating the legal expertise and ability of attorneys to resolve claims and protect the City from fraudulent claims.', 150, 'Strong wins in the original hearings reduces the amount of appeals that will be filed thus reducing additional resources needed', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1891, 224, 2025, 1180, NULL, 1172, NULL, 1164, NULL, 330, NULL, 3846, 'The factors that impacted the FY25 actual data was staffing capacity and expertise (ability to resolve claims) and volume of workplace incidents.', 3600, 'Increased volume of resolved/closed claims reduces amount of resources used (attorney''s, time, additional legal services/fees) and possibly returns employees back to the workforce', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1892, 225, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Data for this KPI is provided via reports from the Workers Compensation Commission, which are distributed on an annual basis. Therefore, we are unable to provide quarterly data at this time.', 0.42, 'We recognized those issues that we could not win and to fight for apportionment at later hearings rather than frustrate the Commission with unnecessary hearings on compensability or to resolve those matters earlier on and limit the City’s future exposure.', 0.25, 'Limiting the City''s exposure by increasing number of cases won before going to hearing', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1893, 226, 2025, 662174, NULL, 640016, NULL, 654978, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2625909, 'The increase in circulation numbers in FY2025 was driven by continued increased shifts in allocation of the materials budget toward electronic circulating materials i.e., ebooks, eaudio and evideo. Ecirculation increase 24% over fiscal year 2024.', 1850000, 'With rolling building closures to address maintenance issues and branch renovations, it is not expected that library usage can expand in FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1894, 227, 2025, 26669, NULL, 27719, NULL, 24575, NULL, NULL, NULL, 123617, 'In FY25, several library locations were closed for renovation; however, program statistics remained steady from FY24. We attribute this to the development of stronger internal program policies and procedures, enhanced staff training, and a new statistics reporting system to ensure greater accuracy.', 110000, 'With rolling building closures to address maintenance issues and branch renovations, it is not expected that library usage can expand in FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1895, 228, 2025, 1955, NULL, 1606, NULL, 1949, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8564, 'With the exception of Housing Navigators, all social impact programs experienced >4% participation growth in FY25. As we continue these programs, we have been able to make more data-driven decisions about program placement, scheduling & promotion, building awareness and strengthening participation.', 5300, 'With rolling building closures to address maintenance issues and branch renovations, it is not expected that library usage can expand in FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1896, 229, 2025, 320157, NULL, 293408, NULL, 296552, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1207984, 'FY 25 Targets were established based on the number of ongoing HVAC projects taking place in branches that included Northwood and Herring Run in addition to the closure of the Forest Park Branch. In addition, the Brooklyn Branch was also closed due to an interior Refresh that was funded by ARPA.', 975000, 'With rolling building closures to address maintenance issues and branch renovations, it is not expected that library usage can expand in FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
