    (1899, 232, 2025, 18, NULL, 16, NULL, 15, NULL, 15, 'This should not be used cumulatively, the same 15 agencies participated Q1, Q2, Q3', 18, NULL, 11, 'In FY 2024, one new Stat was started which increased the number of participating agencies. In addition, additional agencies have begun attending existing Stats as the scope of meetings adjusts to reflect leadership priorities. Both of these trends are expected to continue into FY2025.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1900, 234, 2025, 29, NULL, 26, NULL, 26, NULL, 23, 'Data is actuals. We will provide an average at final submission.', 26, NULL, 18, 'One new Stat was added in FY2024 that will meet monthly. In addition, one Stat previously met monthly but began meeting twice per month in FY2024. Both of these trends are expected to continue into FY2025.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1901, 235, 2025, 157, NULL, 89, NULL, 125, NULL, 116, 'I''m not sure why this is set as an average but the FY25 totals represent an average for the four quarters.', 122, NULL, 30, 'The target number of inspections was identified based on FY2023 and FY2024 trends in staff availability and capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1902, 240, 2025, 124, NULL, 124, NULL, 137, NULL, NULL, 'MOAAME is currently on track to meet its FY25 target for the number of participants initiated into the intake and case management process. The datafreflects the office''s continued commitment to engaging disconnected youth comprehensive supports and resources through personalized personal growth and coordinated wraparound services.', 160, NULL, 150, 'The objective for FY25 is to achieve a 10% growth in recruitment, intake and engagement for the Connect 2 Success program.  The target and actual outcome will be evident in the  target figures. The success results will be evaluated according to the percentage or number of each corresponding performance metric', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1903, 241, 2025, 0.85, NULL, 0.85, NULL, 0.83, NULL, NULL, 'Each quarter, MOAAME has consistently engaged participants in programming, services, and supportive interventions designed to help them achieve two or more goals outlined in their individualized Personal Growth Plans. This intentional approach ensures that youth/young adult receive targeted support aligned with their developmental needs, fostering measurable progress in their personal, academic, and employment pathways.', 0.85, NULL, 0.77, 'MOAAME selected this target percentage based on the attainment of a baseline rate of 70% in FY23.  The decision to select a 5% increment for this performance metric was based on an increase in the number of participants who enrolled and actively engaged with the Connect 2 Success program during FY23._x000D_
