    (1904, 242, 2025, 0.72, NULL, 0.72, NULL, 0.72, NULL, NULL, '(MOAAME actively engages young adults in workforce development and job-readiness programs. Through strategic partnerships with the Mayor’s Office of Employment Development (MOED), various City agencies, and local employers, MOAAME supports participants in securing employment opportunities. pathways.', 0.72, NULL, 0.75, 'MOAAME selected this performance objective for the fiscal year 2025 based on performance levels of FY23, and the recommendations provided by supported partnerships. The indicator focuses on sustaining service level performance and achieving positive outcomes for the youth and young adults who are enrolled and engaged in Connect 2 Success.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
