    (1906, 244, 2025, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 0.67, NULL, NULL, 'During the first quarter, MOAAME staff assisted ten youth in securing employment. All ten maintained their employment for at least 30 days and remained employed through the second quarter, demonstrating sustained workforce engagement. In the third quarter, two additional young adults obtained employment, both of whom maintained their positions for a minimum of 30 days._x000D_
