We held a hiring event in July for both the 311 and DHCD call centers. The training classes began 8/4 and run 6 and 5 weeks,respectively. Also, the SYE initiative will end in early September. Between these two factors, we anticipate meeting our target starting in September. To mitigate this from occurring in the future, recruitment for a new 311 class will begin once there are 4 vacancies.', 0.87, 'Factors that impacted % of calls being answered in 60 seconds include inclement weather, roadwork, power outages etc.  Weather, seasonal events, city operations and service delivery, communications (press conferences) and public awareness, calendar driven impacts .', 0.9, 'Collecting and analyzing 311''s data trends each year helped us arrive at a challenging yet attainable goal.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1922, 266, 2025, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 3, '311 exceeded the target by adequately managing call routing, putting the customer experience first and empowering the team. We also began a targeted effort of a 30/60/90 day follow up process with new hires, training reminders sent through email to staff and refresher training.', 5, 'Collecting and analyzing 311''s data trends each year helped us arrive at a challenging yet attainable goal.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1923, 267, 2025, 38, NULL, 17, NULL, 13, NULL, 47.21, 'The key factors driving this deterioration are:_x000D_
_x000D_
1.	Staffing vacancies: Of the 46-311 agents, currently we are only staffed at 72% due to:_x000D_
_x000D_
a.	4 agents temporarily reassigned to the DHCD call center to expand operations;_x000D_
_x000D_
b.	8 agent positions vacant; and,_x000D_
_x000D_
c.	1 agent serving as an acting supervisor._x000D_
_x000D_
2.	Unfunded Support of SYE (Summer Youth Engagement) requires us to extend hours until 2AM Friday and Saturday. To cover this initiative 4 agents that typically cover the 2-6 pm time had to be shifted to start at 6 pm to support this initiative._x000D_
_x000D_
3.	Leave usage by staff increases during the summer_x000D_
