    (1931, 280, 2025, 5679, NULL, 6271, NULL, 4117, NULL, 3448, 'This metric is an aggregate of counts from various programs: Back2School, LeadHership, AFRAM KidsZone, and Scholar Athletes Award Ceremony attendance (counted with a clicker at the event entrance),  and interactions between students and Safe Passage personnel (as reported by partner organizations).', 18767, 'Fiscal 2025 data included engagements between Safe Passage personnel and youth. Monthly reports submitted by Safe Passage partners have poor data quality due to 1) differences in understanding of what counts as an engagement and 2) lack of a consistent method for data collection/tallying.', NULL, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
