    (1935, 284, 2025, 88, NULL, 95, NULL, 91, NULL, 141, 'Method: Filter to cases that were in any of the statuses below either when the reporting period started or at any point during the reporting period. Deduplicate on Case ID. Statuses include "Approved", "Completed", "Open", "Applied", and "Pending"  _x000D_
