    (1940, 291, 2025, 32.5, NULL, 12.4, NULL, 26.1, NULL, 18.3, '"FY 25 - Total" is the average amount of days it took for a certification application review in FY25.', 22, 'The FY25 actual of 22 days reflects fluctuations in application volume, staffing capacity, and workflow efficiency. Increased outreach contributed to steady application submissions, while operational improvements helped manage processing time.', 30, 'This number was choosen to continue to provide efificent reviews of certification applications.  The 30 day target is supported by our FY23 data and will continue to challenge the team to render these decisions efficiently.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
