    (1947, 333, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 160, 'FY25 vendor participation reﬂects strong demand and continued operations of the Baltimore Farmers Market._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 132, 'Baltimore Farmers Market has a significant impact on the local agricultural economy, food and beverage businesses from Baltimore and beyond, and the creative economy through the participation of artisans. The number of businesses who participate in the Market reflects both the physical scale and indirectly assesses the economic impact of the Market.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1948, 334, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'Public art installations were not implemented during FY25 due to program timing and project scheduling._x000D_
_x000D_', 0.9, 'We were tracking public art at the Community Statistical Area level and wanted to achieve a deeper level of analysis. We can then ensure a more equitable distribution of resources across neighborhoods and city blocks.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1949, 335, 2025, 0.33, NULL, 0.58, NULL, 0.7, NULL, 0.51, NULL, 0.55, 'FY25 results reﬂect grant awards to organizations and artists that identify as Black or Black-led within the Creative Baltimore Fund._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 0.65, 'This measure was collaboratively proposed and agreed upon by BOPA and the Office of Performance and Innovation, in an effort to enhance mutual equity goals. At minimum, BOPA intends for its grantmaking to reflect the demographic breakdown of the City of Baltimore. In future years, we intend to use this measure as a vehicle for advancing equity for underrepresented groups.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1950, 336, 2025, 0.33, NULL, 0.63, NULL, 0.5, NULL, 0.72, NULL, 0.63, 'FY25 results reﬂect grant awards to artists and organizations identifying as women or women-led within Creative Baltimore Fund programs._x000D_
_x000D_', 0.55, 'This measure was collaboratively proposed and agreed upon by BOPA and the Office of Performance and Innovation, in an effort to enhance mutual equity goals. At minimum, BOPA intends for its grantmaking to reflect the demographic breakdown of the City of Baltimore. In future years, we intend to use this measure as a vehicle for advancing equity for underrepresented groups.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1951, 337, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 110, 'FY25 reﬂects continued leveraging of City funding through stable program operations and partnerships._x000D_
_x000D_', 110, 'BOPA hopes that with the return of Artscape and other large events, the City''s return on its investment in our programs and services will be closer to pre-pandemic numbers.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1952, 338, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'FY25 representation reﬂects curatorial programming that includes Latinx artists and cultural programming at the facility.', NULL, 'BOPA aims to ensure that the artists featured in programming at Bromo are reflective of the communities we serve, with a particular focus on under-represented groups in visual art such as Black and Brown, older artists (50+), and women.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1953, 339, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.89, 'FY25 occupancy reﬂects tenant leasing activity and available studio capacity within the facility._x000D_
_x000D_', 1, 'This continues to be an impactful measure for success of the Tower to engage the surrounding communities and their residents in need. Safe, affordable work space is a continuously articulated need by artists.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (1954, 340, 2025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4332, 'FY25 attendance reﬂects participation in tours, events, artwalk programming, and otherpublic engagement activities hosted at the Bromo Seltzer Arts Tower._x000D_
_x000D_', 8000, 'While BOPA''s exhibition programming has increased visitorship a few times a year, we are opting for a more conservative increase in our target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
