_x000D_', 133, 'This service was able to exceed the target due to having the support of the Equity Legislative Analyst and his work on providing opportunity to review and comment on legislation and policy. His efforts ensured that key stakeholders were consistently informed and engaged throughout the process.', 42, 'This target aligns with the division''s historical performance related to equity policy and program analysis and our intention to continue steadily expanding our reviewing capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2014, 406, 2025, 4, NULL, 13, NULL, 14, NULL, 20, 'This measure is reflective of aggregate outreach data from the The Equity Division in addition to three additional commissions ( Mayor''s Commission on Disabilities, Women''s Commission and the Veteran''s Commission) that align under the Equity umbrealla until approved for having unique cost centers and three distinct service areas.', 51, 'The target was exceeded in large part due to the support of the Outreach Division, whose efforts helped to streamline and standardize outreach processes across the service. This collaboration allowed for a more consistent and efficient approach to engaging with communities and stakeholders.', 14, 'Only 7 total are required by ordinance. The goal includes 2 aditional MCD meetings, one additional public forum, and 4 additional MCD committee meetings.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2015, 407, 2025, 0, NULL, 3, NULL, 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 5, 'This performance metric was met._x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 5, 'This target reflects the number of trainings processed by the CRC under Article IV and Title VII.  This target increases outreach and education components to city agencies and aids in the reduction of EEO complaints.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2016, 408, 2025, 0, NULL, 3, NULL, 2, NULL, 0, NULL, 5, 'Education and outreach meetings performance metrics were met in 2025.  Community Relations Commission was able to met this metric by participating and organizing various community based events, Fair Housing Month, Civil Rights week, joint activities with State agencies and other resource fairs.', 5, 'This target is following Article IV of the Baltimore City Code §2-4 (1)', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2017, 409, 2025, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, 'CRC Commissioners are not in session for the month of Aug which leads to no hearings in Q1_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
