Scheduling hearings with other agencies is a challenge that CRC staff is working on.', 2, 'Fiscal year 2025 data for informational and public hearings were lower than target because of scheduling conflicts.', 4, 'This target is following Article IV of the Baltimore City Code §2-4 (10)', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2018, 410, 2025, 8, NULL, 0, NULL, 17, NULL, 5, 'CRC has been short staffed, but is on track to reach the goal of 50, with active cases that the CRC staff are preparing to close._x000D_
_x000D_
