_x000D_
CRC staffing challenges required a downward moditification to 35 from 50.  The EEOC contract will close 35 complaints.', 23, 'FY 2025 data target was impacted by shortage of staff.', 50, 'This target reflects the no. of complaints closed by the CRC within a fiscal year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2019, 411, 2025, 0.5, NULL, 0.5, NULL, 0.2, NULL, 0.5, 'The Community Relations Commission lost an investigator during Q3 and Q4.', 0.43, 'This performance metric was met.', 0.5, 'This target will reduce the time to resolve complaints and provide better service to complainants.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2020, 412, 2025, 16, NULL, 15, NULL, 16, NULL, 24, 'Q1- 13 ACC meetings, 3 PAB meetings; Q2- 11 ACC meetings, 3 PAB meetings, 1 PAD Civil Rights Week Event; Q3- 13 ACC meetings, 3 PAB meetings_x000D_
_x000D_
