_x000D_
_x000D_
With Cleaning having its own SLA, the 90% target tracks with operation ontime rate for CY23', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2078, 471, 2025, 1548, NULL, 1003, NULL, 770, NULL, 1342, 'Increase in citizen complaints related to rats, based on SRs, was higher than expected due to a lack of education on rat behavior and identification of rat activity. Since then the operation has been proactive about providing more education on rat abatement to the public in addition to conducting a pilot program for an alternate pest control method._x000D_
_x000D_', 4663, 'Increase in citizen complaints related to rats, based on SRs, was higher than expected due to rat behavior and identification of rat activity by residents. We have been proactive in social media regarding residents using 311 to submit Ratrubout SRs.  Also, we participated in several community townha', 4000, 'No change in target.  Operation historically averages 5,300 in total SRs and compared to FY22 the numbers are trending down_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
