    (2082, 475, 2025, 0.9255, NULL, 0.9655, NULL, 0.7643, NULL, 0.8747, 'Now that we have both summer and winter plans in place to ensure the health and safety of our employees, there are occasions when we must pause routes and complete them the following day. The implementation of the MOSH heat illness plans, designed to protect our employees'' health and well-being, has also contributed to an increase in service requests and the time required to complete them._x000D_
