    (2083, 476, 2025, 35853.36, NULL, 34355.88, NULL, 32057.25, NULL, 35273.69, 'The actual tons of mixed refuse collected by routine services, as indicated by scale tickets, fell short of the target because we expected a reduction in mixed refuse along with an increase in curbside recycling._x000D_
_x000D_', 137540, 'Trash was collected as residents produced it. The actual tons of mixed refuse collected by routine services, as indicated by scale tickets, fell short of the target because we expected a reduction in mixed refuse along with an increase in curbside recycling.', 152000, 'Increased target based on historical data  for Mixed Refuse collections averages 152K', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2084, 477, 2025, 6700.53, NULL, 6508.07, NULL, 6387.62, NULL, 6371.53, 'The operations acquired additional fleet   (80 load packers) and increased staffing which allowed us to meet our targeted goal._x000D_
_x000D_', 25968, 'Factors that led to meeting and exceeding the target were staffing and contamination efforts. The operation acquired additional fleet   (80 load packers) and increased staffing which allowed us to meet our targeted goal.', 23000, 'Adjusted the target based on historical data for recycling collections never exceeding 23K', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2085, 478, 2025, 338258.77, NULL, 300377.59, NULL, 298224.85, NULL, 357088.59, 'The $1.5 million is a target figure that has not been met since FY23. Ongoing shortages of drivers and equipment have contributed to  delays and a subsequent decline in revenue. Additionally, there have been delays in removing tonnage from our facilities to the disposal site due to wait-times and delays, witht he recieving vendor, which have impacted our ability to dump and return to the facilities in a timely manner._x000D_
_x000D_', 1293950, 'FY 25 target was set high with expected demand to increase.  While the demand exists, operational challenges with a shortage of transfer trailers and extended wait times, slow down the amount of volume we can accept from small haulers at the NWTS.', 1500000, 'Revenue generated from the small haulers'' program has historically failed to meet its target.  However, FY23 saw the objective met_x000D_
