    (2093, 486, 2025, 27.19, NULL, 43.19, NULL, 84.29, NULL, 25.62, NULL, 45, 'Deep Freeze in Previous Year led to a major increase in breaks.', 35, 'Show that efforst to reduce service interuptions are being succesful', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2094, 487, 2025, 0.91, NULL, 0.94, NULL, 0.94, NULL, 0.97, 'The billing unit was down 8 staff members and utilizing overtime to maintain production. Staffing was addressed in our billing operation in the 1st quarter of FY26 to fill 8 vacancies, which resulted in filling 6 Customer Care Analyst II positions.  The job was reposted on 8/8/25 to fill the remaining 2 vacancies.', 0.97, 'Staffing resources in our billing units impacted our FY 25 actuals.', 0.98, 'To ensure the operation is performing based on Call Center Industry Standards', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2095, 488, 2025, 0.9638, NULL, 0.9796, NULL, 0.9721, NULL, 0.9909, NULL, 0.98, 'We were impacted by our staffing resources in our billing unit.', 0.98, 'To ensure the operation is performing based on Call Center Industry Standards', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2096, 489, 2025, 0.95, NULL, 0.95, NULL, 0.95, NULL, 0.94, 'Staffing has been a major factor in the call center. The first round of interviews only yielded 5 new hires to the call center, leaving 10 remaining vacancies for our Customer Care Analyst I role.  Interviews are underway to fill the vacancies.', 0.94, NULL, 0.98, 'To ensure the operation is performing based on Call Center Industry Standards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2097, 490, 2025, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 4.38, NULL, 4, 'Staffing resources impacted our FY25 actuals.', 3, 'To ensure the operation is performing based on Call Center Industry Standards', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2098, 491, 2025, 0.95, NULL, 0.95, NULL, 0.93, NULL, 0.92, 'Staffing has been a major factor in the call center. The first round of interviews only yielded 5 new hires to the call center, leaving 10 remaining vacancies for our Customer Care Analyst I role.  Interviews are underway to fill the vacancies.', 0.93, 'Our call center was impacted by increased calls associated with notifications of waterline insurance coverage plans, the implementation of robocalls for the water4all program and calls from constituents regarding zero consumption or long/excessive bills.', 0.95, 'To ensure the operation is performing based on Call Center Industry Standards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2099, 492, 2025, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 'No issues', 1, 'Goal was met.  All SIU''s were sampled and inspected as required.', 1, '100% inspection and monitoring of SIU''s should always be the goal for permit compliance', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2100, 493, 2025, 0.999, NULL, 0.998, NULL, 0.999, NULL, 1, 'No issues', 0.99, '100% compliance is an aspirational goal not a practical goal.  With over 10,000 possible compliance points in a year, it is very likely that a couple points will be out of compliance.  Thsi is the case for FY25.  99.94 shows excellent performance.', 1, '100% NPDES permit compliance should always be the goal', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2101, 494, 2025, 2784, NULL, 2950, NULL, 2971, NULL, 3208, 'Continuing staffing costs, larger O&M investments due to large scale breakdowns, additional costs associated with T&D at both plants for biosolids.', 2758.37, 'The single biggest factor driving up the cost/MG is the Synagro expense for biosolids handling.  Synagro was not drying biosolids, which increases biosolids removal costs, and thus, expenses for the plants.  A contribuing factor is there was no digestion of solids.', 1935, 'Based on expected flows and additional expenditure costs in FY25 for staffing augmentation, increased commodity costs, O&M burden', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
    (2102, 495, 2025, 170.9, NULL, 157.9, NULL, 171.4, NULL, 189.1, 'Bit of a drought this year', 175, 'Precipitation significantly affects the amount of flow that is treated at the plants. For 2025, we were under the planning trigger(Goal), which is a good thing.', 191, 'Based on 3-year historical trends and expected rain data', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.998111'),
