    (2260, 59, 2026, 603, NULL, 437, NULL, 441, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2100, 'Vacancies within the Office of the Fire Marshal will be filled, the office can handle a higher volume of inspections, reducing any backlog and shortening the time required for each inspection. This increase in capacity allows for more timely inspections and faster issuance of permits, directly addressing customer demand more efficiently.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
