    (2304, 108, 2026, 141, NULL, 77, NULL, 57, '141 homes assessed for health and safety risks (112 home visits and 29 Inspections)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 500, 'The Fiscal 206 target was established based on the past fiscal years data. This goal should remain steady given the hiring of one additional Community Health Educator II and the anticipated hiring of one additional Community Health Worker for FY26. While the FY23 numbers were lower, with the hiring and training of new staff, there should be approximately 500 homes assessed.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2305, 109, 2026, 0.039, NULL, 0.27, NULL, 0.18, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The Fiscal 2026 target was established based on our team having one Environment Sanitarian leave and that we are in the process of hiring two more. The process of hiring is anticipated to take at minimum a few months and training will take up to a year. Given the historical challenges of hiring and training for this role, a slight increase from the FY24 actual data seems the most realistic.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2306, 110, 2026, 0.99, NULL, 0.94, NULL, 0.99, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.95, 'The target will continue to remain at 95% because there are factors that necessitate a visit to the ER that are beyond the control of families and program staff. it is critical that families and staff understand the urgency of reporting to the ER when a child''s condition requires more intensive medical intervention than that which can be provided at home.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2307, 111, 2026, 5132, NULL, 3301, NULL, 1338, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6500, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2308, 112, 2026, 5247, NULL, 3187, NULL, 3301, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7200, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2309, 113, 2026, 247180, NULL, 228430, NULL, 149491, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000000, 'Fiscal 2025 target was established through the review and analysis of both historical data and trends of the past several periods. In addition, the program took into consideration newly implemented outreach strategies that promote a higher level of community engagement, while still maintaining the current level of service provision. Through the new and innovative mixed-method approach to community-centered outreach in targeted areas with high rates of substance use, we are confident that we can increase our encounters and the number of syringes exchanged along with the provision of other services offered by the program.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2310, 114, 2026, 66, NULL, 60, NULL, 35, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 320, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2311, 115, 2026, 176, NULL, 127, NULL, 339, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 525, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2312, 116, 2026, 0.89, NULL, 0.88, NULL, 0.87, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2313, 117, 2026, 1310, NULL, 1215, NULL, 1063, 'We are currently on track to meet the FY26 target. This is a cumulative target that will grow over time.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4157, 'Based on the significant changes in the office of adolescent and reproductive health, we are maintaining our targets from FY25.  We will reassess this target once our strategic plan is complete for FY27.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2314, 118, 2026, 149, NULL, 110, NULL, 143, 'We are on track to meet our FY26 target. This is a snapshot of data, not cumulative and can shift every quarter based on home visitor capacity and client graduation rates.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 150, 'The FY25 target of 150 families served was retained and is based on assuming a full caseload (25 families) for each of M&I''s six nurses. That 25 families consitutes a full caseload is determined by the Nurse-Family Partnership National Service Office and is standard across the US.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2315, 119, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 'We are currently on track to meet our FY26 target', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY25 target of 90% (a high bar given that many Baltimore City families are highly mobile and have significant competing prioties leading to missed visits and lower program retention compared with national averages) was retained and presumed continued strong retention of the nurse home visitors.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2316, 120, 2026, 45021, NULL, 100157, NULL, 88866, 'School was not in regular session during the school summer break.  Therefore the data represents limited activity during July and August, and only one full month for September, rather than the full three-month quarter.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 290000, 'The target was established by reviewing historical performance data over the past few school years, including the number and types of school health suite visits; along with  the changes in school enrolment.  Even though school enrolment has steadily declined from 77,807 in 2022 to 75,811 in 2024, the number of school health suite visits has increased from 239,065 in 2022 to 281,000 in 2024.  although we may anticipate a decrease in enrolment, we expect that as we increase full-time coverage in schools, we will continue to see an increase in health suite visits.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2317, 121, 2026, 0.64, NULL, 0.8, NULL, 0.82, 'School-Based Health Centers were not operational during the school summer break.  Therefore, this data represents activity during the month of September only.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.65, 'While we do anticipate increasing Nurse Practitioner coverage,  we do not expect significant improvement until there is full-time coverage in all sites.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2318, 122, 2026, 0.87, NULL, 0.82, NULL, 0.82, 'School was not in regular session during the school summer break.  Therefore the data represents limited activity during July and August, and only one full month for September rather than the full three-month quarter.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.87, 'We looked at the historical data and determined thatthe return to class rate in 2024 was the highest it has been in recent years, even prior to the pandemic.  However, since there will continue to be sound health related reasons why a student should not remain in school, such as injury or illness, or a communicable condition, we are reluctant to increase this target from Fiscal Year 2024.								_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2319, 123, 2026, 1415, NULL, 1224, NULL, 1352, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2200, 'Fiscal 2026 targets were established using historical program performance data and Fiscal 2025 Q1 program performance data.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2320, 124, 2026, 917, NULL, 1080, NULL, 1285, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1800, 'Fiscal 2026 targets were established using historical program performance data and Fiscal 2025 Q1 program performance data.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2321, 125, 2026, 3384, NULL, 3190, NULL, 3528, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 'Fiscal 2026 targets were established using historical program performance data and Fiscal 2025 Q1 program performance data.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2322, 126, 2026, 51, NULL, 49, NULL, 37, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 45, 'The FY26 targets were established by reviewing previous years targets and assessing the anticipated volume of reporting.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2323, 127, 2026, 0.96, NULL, 0.98, NULL, 0.97, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'FY26 targets were established by reviewing data from pervious year investigations.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2324, 128, 2026, 142, NULL, 222, NULL, 128, 'TIC Training implementation includes weekly sessions with cohorts of up to 25 people per week. Also included are TIC Training sessions with organizations outside of ECHC legislation by request.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 600, 'The program selected its FY26 targets by averaging the actuals for FY22-FY25 (looking at current count for FY25 to date, n=300), which equaled 583. We, then rounded up to the nearest hundred to identify the FY26 target of 600. We feel confident that we will exceed this goal.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2325, 129, 2026, 636, NULL, 184, NULL, 58, 'This number includes individuals participating in suicide prevention workshops and outreach presentations. This number includes students and youth service providers combined. Increased outreach during National Suicide Awareness month in September contributed to the result enabling the program to exceed its performance goal in Q1.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 250, 'Based on FY25 actual, the program set a target that reflected a positive directional goal, that reflected roughly a 10% increase from the previous year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2326, 131, 2026, 0.86, NULL, 0.74, NULL, 0.85, 'Post surveys are administered after each training session. Respondents answering the satisfaction questions are factored into the result. Monthly percentages are calculated then an average of the percentages are calculated quarterly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY26 target was established based on analysis of previous results around sasitsfaction. We have seen trends in the range of 80-95% range for satisfaction. We decided to remain steadfast in selecting 90% as the target, as the program continuously strives to improve the training experience. We are confident that our satisfaction rate will remain within that range for future trainings.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2327, 132, 2026, 0.93, NULL, 0.91, NULL, 0.91, 'Post surveys are administered after each session. Monthly totals are calculated and the average of the quarter are factored into results.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The program established FY26 target by taking the average of the past 2 fiscal years then rounded it to the nearest whole number. We set this target to safely account for a possible decline by a few points in any given period.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
