    (2331, 136, 2026, 1665, NULL, 1578, NULL, 1241, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4000, 'The target is set at 4,000 inspections because the program believes that with the current level of staffing we can conduct this number of inspections. As vacancies are filled for the inspectors the number of inspections will increase.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2332, 137, 2026, 0.99, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 'Syringe disposal SR data was included in this number.  SR was requested to be withdrawn from EIS data.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'The target is set to 100% because our program believes that with the appropriate resources, all complaints can be resolved within the expected timeframe.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2333, 138, 2026, 2, NULL, 2, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The target is still set at 5 because the program believes that there may be an increase in new businesses opening as the economy recovers in a post-Covid world.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2334, 139, 2026, 112, NULL, 188, NULL, 144, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000, 'The FY26 target was established by considering the number of tobbaco outlets in Baltimore City as well as how to better approach the contract process in FY26.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2335, 141, 2026, 590, NULL, 544, NULL, 456, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6000, 'The FY26 target was established based on reviewing FY24 and FY25 data, and taking current staffing and strategies, as listed above, into account.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2336, 142, 2026, 0.941, NULL, 0.68, NULL, 0.7, 'Percent of viral load suppressed used rather than undetectable. _x000D_
_x000D_
those with suppressed VL have a VL of <200 and undetectable VL have a VL of <30. Percent undetectable for the same time period is 72.5%', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY26 goal was established to align with our Ending the HIV Epidemic goal for viral load suppression and through an analysis of previous trends.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2337, 143, 2026, 0.71, NULL, 0.64, NULL, 0.6, 'there were 22 interviews conducted among 35 newly diagnosed HIV patients. However 3 refused interview and 1 person was deceased. removing these from the denominator gives 71% Interviewed', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'We are adjusting this target so that it is the same as the target the state has established for this work. The Maryland Department of Health evaluates BCHD''s team on this metric quarterly.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2338, 144, 2026, 8827, NULL, 12056, NULL, 9643, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 44000, 'Numbers better reflect FY24 numbers with an anticipation for continued increased assistance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2339, 145, 2026, 7112, NULL, 9578, NULL, 9651, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10500, 'Numbers reflect elevated participation numbers based on continued program expansion.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2340, 146, 2026, 13827, NULL, 19699, NULL, 15503, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20000, 'Numbers reflect elevated participation numbers based on continued program expansion.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2341, 147, 2026, 7066, NULL, 9968, NULL, 5597, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 25000, 'The FY 2026 target was derived by averaging the call volume for FY 2022- FY 2024, to account for possible fluctuations in a given fiscal year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2342, 148, 2026, 278, NULL, 280, NULL, 280, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1300, 'The FY 2026 target assumes full staffing of the program team, allowing it to increase facility visitation, resulting in generation of more inquiries from residents and  complaint cases to be resolved.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2343, 149, 2026, 326, NULL, 294, NULL, 239, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 780, 'The FY 2026 target assumes that the FY 2026 volume of counseling  service requests will be consistent with recent trends in the program.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2344, 150, 2026, 160, NULL, 160, NULL, 170, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 145, 'The FY 2026 target anticipates continued growth of the volunteer roster  consistent with the FY 2024 actuals, while recognizing that program growth may slow, depending on factors beyond our control, including the need of older Baltimore City resident to find employment to maintain financial security.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2345, 151, 2026, 17, NULL, 15, NULL, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 40, 'Baltimore City is the largest jurisdiction, thus requiring more rescources to meet industry standards of service.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2346, 152, 2026, 16, NULL, 24, NULL, 16, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 75, 'This target was based on the program returing to normal operating funds, the enhanced grant funds are not guaranteed from year to year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2347, 153, 2026, 4, NULL, 10, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 25, 'The program has a set number of participant slots.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2348, 154, 2026, 21, NULL, 25, NULL, 25, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 18, 'The grant funding determines program capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2349, 155, 2026, 1638, NULL, 1659, NULL, 1651, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6500, 'The projected growth in participants is consistent with recent trends in the program.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2350, 156, 2026, 2272, NULL, 2165, NULL, 2017, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2500, 'The goal of the program is to establish stability and continued service for existing sites. The goal of 2,500 reflects the current projected budget capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2351, 157, 2026, 873, NULL, 848, NULL, 901, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000, 'Levels were established based on the expectation of ARPA funding ending and needing to continue to maintain a slightly elevated level of service compared to pre-pandemic participation based on existing need.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2352, 158, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.91, 'The goal is to maintain a high level of service and satisfaction for the program. Continued satisfaction means continued participation which will ensure that older adults will continue to have access to food and participate in socialization. The current meal contract has been put out to bid and the scoring will include participant preferences in hopes of increasing meal quality and participant satisfaction.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2353, 159, 2026, 1176, NULL, 1284, NULL, 2139, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4500, 'Based on prior years’ actual results. Funding is expected to remain level, so services will as well.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2354, 160, 2026, 0.9, NULL, 0.9, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'DHCD seeks to build community capacity to ensure that small community-based organizations are able to take full advantage of the renovation of vacant properties. This metric was chosen to measure the effectiveness of CCG funds to emerging organization in helping those organizations build capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2355, 161, 2026, 0.56, NULL, 0.54, NULL, 0.662, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'Changing the PM to reflect “the % of sub-recipients and City agencies that report on their contractual goals/accomplishments within 30 days of the end of each quarter” is a better measure of the service''s responsibility to enforce grant compliance and reporting.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2356, 162, 2026, 15, NULL, 15, NULL, 15, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 30, 'This number is dictated by the licensing by the State of Maryland', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2357, 163, 2026, 1984, NULL, 2909, NULL, 4200, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3500, 'Estimates of anticipated staffing cost, service contracts, food and all other programmatic related cost.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2358, 164, 2026, 0.9, NULL, 0.9, NULL, 0.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'This was established by reviewing attendance for 2024 and goalsetting for 2026', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2359, 165, 2026, 36, NULL, 28, NULL, 84, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 270, 'This metric’s goals were established by current interest levels in weatherization programming.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2360, 166, 2026, 3, NULL, 3, NULL, 16, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 150, 'FY26 targets mirror previous years’ targets', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2361, 167, 2026, 12, NULL, 31, NULL, 32, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'This metric’s goals were established by current disqualification rates of homes audited to weatherization services completed.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2362, 168, 2026, 51, NULL, 55, NULL, 34, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 150, '150 is based on historical actual data of the last 4 years achieved by the program (145) with a slight increase projected due to lower interest rates', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2363, 169, 2026, 170, NULL, 190, NULL, 164, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 725, 'Average of the last 3 years', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2364, 170, 2026, 0.76, NULL, 0.8, NULL, 0.73, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.6, '60% target is established based on the last five years actuals', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2365, 171, 2026, 39753, NULL, 36447, NULL, 39123, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 190000, 'We analyzed historical inspection data which consisted of re-inspection of open notices, 311 service requests and inspector-initiated request for action while factoring in staffing variations, seasonal fluctuations, and special projects to establish this target. Timely response to resident complaints is key to providing the customer service we believe every citizen expects and deserves.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2366, 172, 2026, 0.82, NULL, 0.93, NULL, 0.94, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'The analysis of historical SR data, while factoring in staffing variations, seasonal fluctuations, and special projects are factors used to establish this target.  Timely response to resident complaints is essential to providing good customer service.  Experience tells us that there will always be some matters beyond our control that allow a SR to go beyond the expected time to close.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2367, 173, 2026, 0.53, NULL, 0.49, NULL, 0.5, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'This target was set based on historical data initiated by constituent concerns funneled through the City Council, the Mayor’s Office, Fire Department, and Department of Public Works', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2368, 174, 2026, 6522, NULL, 6507, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1800, 'FY26 metric is set based on current number of registered electrical, gas, demolition and onsite contractors currently registered with the CIty.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2369, 175, 2026, 36671, NULL, 40648, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 60000, 'We are maintaining the FY 24 and FY 25 goals as this is where we believe the registration numbers should be at this time in the program. We do not see a benefit in lowering the numbers and will continue to work to increase the number of registered properties.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2370, 176, 2026, 0.311, NULL, 0.523, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.46, 'We believe with outreach and enforcement activities we can realistically see a 10% increase in the number of licensed units.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2371, 177, 2026, 6496, NULL, 12110, NULL, 75000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 35000, 'Given the consistent revenue estimates over the past two years, we relied on prior year goals when planning for fiscal year 2026', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2372, 178, 2026, 31, NULL, 38, NULL, 2.86, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20, 'Given the consistent revenue estimates over the past two years, we relied on prior year goals when planning for fiscal year 2026', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2373, 179, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 50, 'We remain on track to support homeownership projects at consistent levels, maintaining activity for creating and subsidizing affordable units.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2374, 180, 2026, 154, NULL, 218, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 300, 'Due to a lower estimated revenue compared to previous years, we will need to reduce allocations for rental projects, which in turn will lower the amount of city dollars contributed.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2375, 181, 2026, 0.17, NULL, 0.29, NULL, 0.2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'DHCD proposes maintaining a target of completing 80% of property dispositions within 120 days for FY26. This target supports the continued efficient transfer of City-owned properties while accounting for the additional time required to negotiate and finalize more complex dispositions.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2376, 182, 2026, 0.43, NULL, 0.237, NULL, 0.237, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'DHCD is committed to maintaining its compliance target of 50% of properties. While efforts to surpass this goal continue, the target has been set with careful consideration of current staffing constraints to ensure realistic and sustainable outcomes.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2377, 183, 2026, 178.1, NULL, 158.4, NULL, 154.2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 250, 'DHCD has adjusted its FY26 target downward while maintaining a level higher than the FY24 actuals. This adjustment reflects recognition that enhanced internal capacity alone does not guarantee a corresponding increase in external capacity. If external partners are unable to meet the demands of higher filing volumes, it could significantly affect the timeline for completing in rem acquisitions.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2378, 184, 2026, 81, NULL, 115, NULL, 1100, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1100, 'DHCD has adjusted its FY26 target upward to more closely align with the Mayor’s commitment to acquire 1,000 vacants per year. Similar to In Rem, this adjustment reflects recognition that we can enhance internal capacity, however, the assignment of more acquisitions does not guarantee a corresponding increase in external capacity from title companies, abstractors, appraisals, and circuit court.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2379, 185, 2026, 23, NULL, 10, NULL, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100, 'The 2026 goals align with HUD grant benchmarks for the Lead', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2380, 186, 2026, 24, NULL, 43, NULL, 38, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100, 'Based on the number of anticipated legacy homeowners served in FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2381, 187, 2026, 47, NULL, 52, NULL, 158, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 320, 'Based upon anticipated grant funding and FY25 goals a modest increase is suggested to the 2026 fiscal year target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2382, 188, 2026, 96, NULL, 59, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 515, 'FY26 goal is based on the three-year average of demolitions and stabilizations started.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2383, 189, 2026, 16410, NULL, 16040, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 75000, 'The fiscal year 2026 target is based on the three-year average.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2384, 190, 2026, 0.929, NULL, 0.938, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'FY26 target is set to maintain a high level of service.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2385, 191, 2026, 7881, NULL, 8141, NULL, 7726, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 40500, 'FY26 goal is based on the three-year average of permits issued.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2386, 192, 2026, 12385, NULL, 12187, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 11800, 'The FY26 goal is in line with the City and State goal to see a reduction in vacant properties and reflective of the current city and state programs are currently being rolled out in FY25 and the beginning of FY26. As we do not anticipate meeting the FY25 goal of (12,199), the FY26 goal is made in relation to where we expect to end FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2387, 193, 2026, 19, NULL, 21, NULL, 16, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'The FY26 target was established by reviewing the FY24 actual data of waitlist vs. Personnel.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2388, 195, 2026, 218, NULL, 215, NULL, 324, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 375, 'This FY26 target was established by reviewing old metrics and right sizing number based on the realignment of duties and responsibilities', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2389, 196, 2026, 406442, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400000, 'This number is based off the last three years of actuals of 393,657 meals served with a sight increase, which can be achieved with several additional sites.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2390, 197, 2026, 225, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 210, 'SFSP total of 210 sites is based off the actual data of sites over the past four years.   _x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2391, 198, 2026, 0.08, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.09, 'The Fiscal 2026 target was established based on actuals over the last three years', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2392, 204, 2026, 0.82, NULL, 0.75, NULL, 0.82, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The target is based on historical data, performance, and anticipated challenges. The adoption of Workday Learning continues to provide great opportunity and ease for employees to enroll in courses, however, with enrollment continuing to rise, completion is often impacted.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2393, 205, 2026, 40, NULL, 54, NULL, 54, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 30, 'The FY 2026 target is consistent with the FY 2025 target. Until baseline annual data is established the target will remain the same.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2394, 206, 2026, 13.57, NULL, 10.63, NULL, 2.13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15, 'The target for FY 2026 is based on the first quarter data for job requisitions during Fiscal 2025. The Office of Recruitment reviewed 859 job requisitions in the first quarter of FY 2025 (24 candidates on average, ranging from 1 candidate per job requisition to up 639 candidates for a job requisition).', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2395, 207, 2026, 0.44, NULL, 0.7, NULL, 0.85, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.05, 'This target is based on historical trends along with anticipated changes and challenges. The current Leadership Pathway learning program was phased out in July 2024 for necessary revisions and the revised program will relaunch in March 2025. The program will only target 80 supervisors each year across 4 cohorts (20 supervisors per cohort). The target is based on 80 per year divided by the population of supervisors while anticipating enrollment in the Supervisor Essentials.  DHR made the decision to relaunch the Leadership Pathway based on learner feedback, the potential for increased networking amongst people leader and that higher more frequent engagement leads to increased comprehension, application and completion.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2396, 208, 2026, 0.57, NULL, 0.71, NULL, 0.72, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.6, 'The target was based on the estimated number of current city employees that are city residents.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2397, 209, 2026, 0.0785, NULL, 0.0858, NULL, 0.0567, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.63, 'The target is based on the proposed available catalog of wellness events for employees that will be available during Fiscal 2026. DHR Wellness has over 200 different options in its wellness catalog that events are chosen from and agencies can request for special wellness events. This is in addition to the annual events such in person and virtual wellness fairs and other large-scale events.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2398, 210, 2026, 0.96, NULL, 0.97, NULL, 0.96, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The target is set based on combining industry benchmarking for the Customer Satisfaction Score (CSAT), American Customer Satisfaction Index (ACSI), and American Productivity & Quality Center (APQC) within the training industry. Though benchmarking recognizes 74.4% as the US customer satisfaction score, due to the importance of education and training our target is increased. Overall, we have increased the target due to historical data, and are optimistic of, however are aware of two variables that may negatively impact our satisfaction rating. Number one, there is an increase of agency created trainings, that the Office of Learning and Development does not craft. The production and requirement to complete these trainings may negatively impact satisfaction. Number two, in the coming year more marketing and further integration of our service providers content will be more easily accessed through Workday Learning. Though it is quality content, the learner''s satisfaction of the new content is not yet known. The target is a goal, and though it''s attainable under perfect conditions it''s a challenge due to unknown factors that may arise and our continued use of the same content.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2399, 211, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'Data only provided at year end. Quarterly data not available.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.97, 'The target is based on historical data from the Employee Assistance Program (EAP) and industry standards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2400, 212, 2026, 0.01, NULL, 0.006, NULL, 0.0072, 'N/A - Open enrollment for benefits started at the beginning of Q2. Data will be reported for Q2.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.2, 'The Fiscal 2026 target is consistent with prior year targets. As this is a relatively new target DHR plans to keep it consistent until it is achieved, when it will then be adjusted. As more individuals retire from the city over time and are used to working with Workday, DHR anticipates the number of retirees using Workday to complete their benefits enrollment versus sending in paper versions will increase.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2401, 213, 2026, 0.79, NULL, 0.892, NULL, 0.8439, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The Fiscal 2026 target is established based on prior year trends in actuals. DHR is realistic that until the Citywide salary study is implemented the number of requests for classification and compensation analyses may remain higher than targeted impeding the Office’s ability to have a higher completion target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2402, 214, 2026, 10334, NULL, 6839, NULL, 8573, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10000, 'The target is set based on historical data trends, performance, anticipated improvement, and city-wide adoption to Workday Learning. The target is a goal, and though attainable under perfect conditions it’s still a challenge due to unknown factors that may arise. Targets are also generated with the assumption that access to packaged content remains, and Working Learning access remains.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2403, 215, 2026, 714, NULL, 424, NULL, 382, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000, 'DHR is maintaining the same target as FY 2024 and FY 2025 as ideally the number of class and comp projects should decline over time as salary studies are implemented.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2404, 216, 2026, 66, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 215, 'The FY26 target for this performance metric was established based on service goal #1: By June 30, 2026, fully implement the claim management system to include all personnel trained and actively utilizing the platform to process claims and collect data.  The targeted total was decreased to account for the estimated 15% decrease in the need for litigation of liability claims and the claims unit (CBI) implements the claim management system.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2405, 217, 2026, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'The FY26 target for this service was established to align with the service goal #1: By June 30, 2026, fully implement the claim management system to include all personnel trained and actively utilizing the platform to process claims and collect data.  Implementation of the software will improve the efficiency of the claim process, therefore supporting the increase of response time to 100% and reducing the need for additional litigating action by 15%.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2406, 218, 2026, 0.2972, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.03, 'The total amount of damages claimed is not within the City’s control.  State law now permits plaintiffs to plead a generic ad damnum of “more than $75,000” in the Circuit Court, however the Labor & Employment team effectively defends the City''s position on these claims to reduce the payout amount.  As a result, we expect that the targeted payout for damages claimed will remain under 5% for FY26._x000D_
