    (2416, 228, 2026, 2568, NULL, 1840, NULL, 1683, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6000, 'Projected for FY2026 and utilized the projection in tandem with FY2024 actuals to determine a manageable target', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2417, 229, 2026, 274448, NULL, 262916, NULL, 298730, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000000, 'Projected for FY2026 and utilized the projection in tandem with FY2024 actuals to determine a manageable target', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2418, 230, 2026, 713518, NULL, 684661, NULL, 694095, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2800000, 'Projected for FY2026 and utilized the projection in tandem with FY2024 actuals to determine a manageable target', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2419, 231, 2026, 86, NULL, 86, NULL, 85, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 80, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2420, 232, 2026, 23, NULL, 23, NULL, 23, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2421, 233, 2026, 0.909, NULL, 0.923, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2422, 234, 2026, 33, NULL, 32.5, NULL, 31.67, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15, 'Meetings per quarter—our draft plan is to have 17 Stats totaling 19 CitiStat meetings/month  and twenty in months where a quarterly meeting would occur by November. Because of the build up, we would propose a goal of 15.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2423, 235, 2026, 80, NULL, 57.5, NULL, 40.3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 90, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2424, 240, 2026, 144, NULL, 149, NULL, 153, 'During Q1, the Mayor’s Office of African American Male Engagement (MOAAME) engaged 144 youth and young adults through the Connect 2 Success program. Engagement included intake and assessment, development of personal growth plans, and the establishment of individualized goals and objectives to support participants’ educational, workforce, and program‑year priorities. Participants were assigned credible mentors and resource navigators to provide ongoing guidance and service coordination. Programming also included civic and community engagement activities, participation in special projects, and workforce exposure through One Day’s Work/One Day’s Pay opportunities.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 140, 'Assuming no additional funding is received. MOAAME''s FY26 impact with the same youth and young adults will remain.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2425, 241, 2026, 0.8, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'During Q1, the Mayor’s Office of African American Male Engagement (MOAAME) engaged 144 youth and young adults through the Connect 2 Success program. 137 participants _x000D_
_x000D_
were on task to complete two or more goals. Of those participants, 109 completed two or more goals identified in their personal growth plans.  Note: ( 5-ended participation before 90 days and two have not reached the 90 day mark)._x000D_
_x000D_', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.77, 'FY26 target was establised based upon FY24 actual assuming that no additional funding will be received for positive impact for achieving 2 or more personal goals.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2426, 242, 2026, 0.71, NULL, 0.71, NULL, 0.69, 'During Q1 MOAAME has engaged 144 participants in the Connect 2 Success Program. 102 participants were actively attending school or employed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'FY26 target was establised based upon FY24 baseline and assuming no additional funding for expanded case-management, outreach, and guidance provided by collaborators.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2427, 243, 2026, 0.83, NULL, 0.71, NULL, 0.72, 'During Q1, the MOAAME engaged 142 participants through the Connect 2 Success program. Each participant was assigned a credible mentor, and when appropriate, a resource navigator. Of the 144 participants, 119 had at least one in-person engagement with a mentor during each month of the quarter.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'FY26 target was establised  based upon assuming no additional supplemental funding  will be received to allow MOAAME to expand the frequency of and number of in-person contact between MOAAME staff and/or Credible Mentors and youth and young adults.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2428, 244, 2026, 0.94, NULL, 0.75, NULL, 1, 'During Q1,  17 non-school aged  Connect 2 Success participants applied for obtained employment. 16 were employed for 30 days.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'FY26 target was establised based upon FY24 baseline and assuming no additional funding for expanded case-management, outreach, and guidance provided by collaborators.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2429, 245, 2026, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2430, 246, 2026, 250, NULL, 520, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 16000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2431, 247, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12, 'The Fiscal Year 2026 targets were intentionally designed to remain within our current capacity, be a reflection of past performance, and plan for growth in the key areas that contribute to our mission objectives._x000D_
