    (2450, 272, 2026, 0.99, NULL, 0.99, NULL, 0.99, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.99, '99.8% uptime/availability of results for the City''s public wi-fi network in the following periods of allowed downtime/unavailability: Daily: 2m 53s; Weekly: 20m 9.6s; Monthly: 1h 26m 56s; Quarterly: 4h 20m 49s and Yearly: 17h 23m 16s. Achieving 100% uptime/availability is not practical due to the necessity of scheduled maintenance outages for all network infrastructures.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
