    (2476, 339, 2026, 0.83, NULL, 0.71, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'FY26 target was established based on a combination of historical performance, growing market demand, strategic facility goals, and the desire to ensure ﬁnancial sustainability community impact. Moving in this direction reﬂects a realistic ambition to maximize the use of available studio space while supporting the local arts community and ensuring that the facility is a key resource for Balmore creatives.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2477, 340, 2026, 2456, NULL, 1965, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5000, 'FY26 target was established based on a combination of historical attendance data, program expansion, strategic growth goals, and marketing eﬀorts. This target reﬂects the organization’s ambition to grow its audience, build on past success, and increased engagement through a combination of expanded programming, increased accessibility and improved outreach.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2478, 344, 2026, 3091, NULL, 37995, NULL, 54433, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 148730, 'Using the same methodology applied to FY24 actuals, the FY26 targets were calculated. These attendance projections are based on an estimated 33 in-house events. When contracting an event, we request clients to provide an estimated attendance, which is recorded in our event management system. Upon the event’s conclusion, final attendance figures are also captured in the system. This process allows us to identify variances and analyze them, helping to uncover any significant trends. _x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2479, 345, 2026, 17, NULL, 34, NULL, 21, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 90, 'Each month we extract the event data from our event management system, for events that have a high possibility of occuring. The FY26 target was from the data extraction on 11-22-24. Throughout the fiscal year, the sales team works to book events during the year, so there will generally be a greater number of actualized events than target events.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2480, 346, 2026, 2, NULL, 2.1, NULL, 2.97, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9.7, 'Events with a high probability of occurring between July 1st and June 30th are calculated as part of the relevant fiscal year''s projections. For the FY26 targets, the Convention Center did not include revenue from complimentary events. Each July, the Convention Center provides its in-house, commission-generating partners with a list of potential events to facilitate revenue forecasting. The forecasts from each partner, along with the rental amounts, are then aggregated. If the partner forecasts do not align with historical averages, we adjust by using the average from the last three full years of operation, which for FY26 includes FY24, FY23, and FY19. _x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
_x000D_
Additionally, throughout FY24 and into FY25, the Convention Center completed new partner contracts with more favorable terms. These updated agreements result in higher commission rates compared to the previous structure. Specifically, telecom commissions increased by at least 33%, power commissions by at least 33%, and audiovisual (A/V) commissions by at least 27.6%. Each of these contracts includes commission "kickers" that further increase commissions upon reaching specified milestones. The A/V contract also introduces a new revenue stream from rigging, and in FY25, we will establish a baseline that will be reflected in the FY27 budget.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2481, 347, 2026, 0.9209, NULL, 0.915, NULL, 0.9025, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'The 100% for FY26 is due to the Convention Center always striving to deliver 100% client satisfaction.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2482, 348, 2026, 26580, NULL, 122657, NULL, 169555, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 388743, 'Each month we extract the event data from our event management system, for events that have a high possibility of occurring. The FY26 target was from the data extraction on 11-22-24. Throughout the fiscal year, the sales team works to book events during the year, so there will generally be a greater number of actualized events than target events.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2483, 351, 2026, 0.2894, NULL, 0.2833, NULL, 0.3695, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.27, 'Aligned with navigators on outreach teams', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2484, 352, 2026, 0.1821, NULL, 0.1699, NULL, 0.1725, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.2, 'Outreach team will now be more housing focused', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
