    (2494, 362, 2026, 0.9914, NULL, 0.9865, NULL, 0.989, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.97, 'Increase was due to the ARPA Flex Fund offered by MOHS. It was able to assist households with remaining stably housed', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2495, 363, 2026, 0.0555, NULL, 0.0555, NULL, 0.0615, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.05, 'Slight increase over last year', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2496, 364, 2026, 0.3159, NULL, 0.3196, NULL, 0.333, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.25, 'Slight increase over last year', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2497, 365, 2026, 0.1456, NULL, 0.2024, NULL, 0.2082, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.14, 'MOHS has deployed system improvemet stratgies in flex  funds wihc will assist with rental assistance for up to 6 months and by incorporating diversion at community access points', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2498, 366, 2026, 21, NULL, 15, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'This metric does not have a target. The ECB cannot control the number of people that require and/or choose to use an interpreter. However, we do think it is important to report out the level of engagement that we see with non-English speaking residents.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2499, 367, 2026, 0.62, NULL, 0.69, NULL, 0.16, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'This metric will likely never be 100%. Respondents have conflicts that may push them outside of that 60 day timeframe (traveling, hospitalization, attorney schedules) or volume influxes may cause the ECB to have more hearing requests than docket spaces. Due to this, I kept the FY26 metric at 90%. If we are able to surpass 90% in FY25 (three fiscal years in a row), we will increase the target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2500, 368, 2026, 0.66, NULL, 0.8, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The target will remain at 90%. There is no way to guarantee that the Board will agree with every hearing officer''s decision, but it should be that the majority of cases coming out of the ECB are above reproach.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2501, 369, 2026, 5.53, NULL, 10.15, NULL, 14, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 13, 'Unlike our tax sale metric, we do not have enough data to show a trend. However, we do anticipate this process moving faster with the addition of the Paralegal. With that said, we are reducing the target by one day. If the actuals for FY25 continue to trend downward, we will consider further reductions in the future.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2502, 370, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 24, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 13, 'Based on the actual data from prior fiscal years, the ECB is reducing its target by one day. If the actuals for FY25 continue to trend downward, we will consider further reductions in the future. _x000D_
