It should be noted that the proactive work that we did in FY24 is dependent on proper staffing to do that work. Because of vacancies, we were unable to do that same level of proactive work in F25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
