    (2504, 372, 2026, 510000000, NULL, 549700000, NULL, 574000000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 605000000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2505, 373, 2026, 68, NULL, 54, NULL, 55, 'The decrease is due to a large number of projects finishing at the end of FY25 and a project manager was on leave most of the quarter.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 60, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2506, 374, 2026, 889, NULL, 928, NULL, 915, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 925, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2507, 376, 2026, 78, NULL, 106, NULL, 173, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 120, 'MOED collaborates with BCPS to operate the YO Academy, and BCPS refers students who have not been successful in a more traditional academic setting.  The performance targets for the Academy are outlined in MOED’s agreement with BCPS.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2508, 377, 2026, 0.14, NULL, 0.4, NULL, 0.58, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'The FY26 goals for the Blueprint initiative reflect the program’s increasing capacity as staff become established within school buildings and develop relationships to enable student access, since the major limitation to the program’s stated aim of reaching every student is gaining the access needed in the school schedule for Coaches to meaningfully interact with them. Working with BCPS to calculate the percentage of students not deemed chronically absent as of November 2024, we determined that career coaches will be able to gain access to and provide basic services to 85% of students in FY26.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2509, 378, 2026, 0.01, NULL, 0.05, NULL, 0.06, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.72, 'The overall goal for Blueprint is to provide services to all students beginning in grade 6, which means that during the first years of the program, older students, especially those already in high school, will require a certain amount of catch-up work in order to meet the initiative’s goals. This is reflected in the FY26 goal for the number of students expected to complete, or to get on track to complete, an individual employment plan. The partners have conducted a multi-year analysis of information about students in grades 6-10 and established timelines for bringing all students up to standards. As a result, we expect the number of students achieving this goal to continue to increase in FY26.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2510, 379, 2026, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'MOED collaborates with BCPS to operate the YO Academy, and BCPS refers students who have not been successful in a more traditional academic setting.  The performance targets for the Academy are outlined in MOED’s agreement with BCPS.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2511, 380, 2026, 432, NULL, 825, NULL, 1222, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1200, 'The target for Fiscal Year 2026 was established based on several program enhancements and additions. Starting in FY 2026, the FLEX program will be fully implemented, offering expanded services that include a dedicated mental health and substance use provider. The program will also expand to serve two new customer groups: non-custodial parents and justice-involved youth. The inclusion of these non-TANF customer groups is expected to increase the number of individuals served at the Workforce Reception Center.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2512, 381, 2026, 0.42, NULL, 0.41, NULL, 0.37, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.45, 'The target for Fiscal Year 2026 was established based on several program enhancements and additions. Starting in FY 2026, the FLEX program will be fully implemented, offering expanded services that include a dedicated mental health and substance use provider. The program will also expand to serve two new customer groups: non-custodial parents and justice-involved youth. The inclusion of these non-TANF customer groups is expected to increase the number of individuals served at the Workforce Reception Center. _x000D_
_x000D_
