    (2514, 383, 2026, 121, NULL, 274, NULL, 394, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 600, 'FY26 targets were established through a strategic planning process with Community Job Hub network partner organizations, which involved intensive evaluation of both the traffic levels at each location and the outcomes achieved for each service provided to the community. Additionally, MOED took into account the fact that American Rescue Plan (ARPA) funds for this program will sunset in December of 2026, midway through the fiscal year. While we will continue to seek additional funding sources and look for creative ways to continue these services in Baltimore City neighborhoods, we have reduced our service goals in accordance with the anticipated funding reduction.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2515, 384, 2026, 300, NULL, 667, NULL, 883, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1935, 'FY26 job placement targets were established based on center traffic and historical data. MOED plans to focus on occupational training leading to industry recognized credentials; apprenticeships; and workforce opportunities for individuals impacted by the Key bridge callapse, affected by opioid addiction,  and justice involved individuals all leading to employment in high growth high demand industry sectors.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2516, 385, 2026, 441, NULL, 723, NULL, 1195, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 790, 'FY26 targets were established through a strategic planning process with Community Job Hub network partner organizations, which involved intensive evaluation of both the traffic levels at each location and the outcomes achieved for each service provided to the community. Additionally, MOED took into account the fact that American Rescue Plan (ARPA) funds for this program will sunset in December of 2026, midway through the fiscal year. While we will continue to seek additional funding sources and look for creative ways to continue these services in Baltimore City neighborhoods, we have reduced our service goals in accordance with the anticipated funding reduction.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2517, 386, 2026, 8774, NULL, 14370, NULL, 19596, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20000, 'These federal Funds are disbursed from the U.S. Department of Labor and passed through the MD Department of Labor, and the performance measure definitions are outlined in the legislation. The target percentages for participants remaining employed are set based on the WIOA performance negotiations conducted between MOED and the MD Department of Labor, following the WIOA guidelines.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2518, 387, 2026, 0.66, NULL, 0.66, NULL, 0.647, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.62, 'These federal Funds are disbursed from the U.S. Department of Labor and passed through the MD Department of Labor, and the performance measure definitions are outlined in the legislation. The target percentages for participants remaining employed are set based on the WIOA performance negotiations conducted between MOED and the MD Department of Labor, following the WIOA guidelines.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2519, 388, 2026, 0.63, NULL, 0.62, NULL, 0.616, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.62, 'These federal Funds are disbursed from the U.S. Department of Labor and passed through the MD Department of Labor, and the performance measure definitions are outlined in the legislation. The target percentages for participants remaining employed are set based on the WIOA performance negotiations conducted between MOED and the MD Department of Labor, following the WIOA guidelines.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2520, 389, 2026, 806, NULL, 1638, NULL, 2007, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1800, 'The Mayor''s Office of Employment Development has an annual contract with the Maryland Department of Public Safety and Correctional Services (DPSCS) to provide workforce services to previously incarcerated residents looking to return to the workforce, and the goals for the service are set within this agreement. MOED is required to register and serve 1800 justice-involved or returning citizens, of which 500 must be currently under supervision by DPSCS, and to place 400 individuals, 200 under supervision, in jobs.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2521, 390, 2026, 170, NULL, 328, NULL, 407, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'The Mayor''s Office of Employment Development has an annual contract with the Maryland Department of Public Safety and Correctional Services (DPSCS) to provide workforce services to previously incarcerated residents looking to return to the workforce, and the goals for the service are set within this agreement. MOED is required to register and serve 1800 justice-involved or returning citizens, of which 500 must be currently under supervision by DPSCS, and to place 400 individuals, 200 under supervision, in jobs.  _x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2522, 391, 2026, 313, NULL, 448, NULL, 645, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 725, 'Enrollment targets were dropped from 850 to 725 to reflect significant population loss in the areas surrounding the YO Centers demonstrated in prior year’s performance, but not reflected in prior year’s goals.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2523, 392, 2026, 0.19, NULL, 0.21, NULL, 0.4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'The FY26 target remains the same as FY25 since MOED feels confident in its ability to meet these goals.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2524, 393, 2026, 0.15, NULL, 0.29, NULL, 0.25, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'Placement goals have been dropped from 54% to 50% as YO builds a greater focus on providing more intensive supportive services to clients and prioritize ensuring youth have supports and stability necessary to attain and maintain work, rather than focusing on immediate job placement.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2525, 394, 2026, 0.99, NULL, 0.98, NULL, 0.98, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY26 target remains the same as FY25 since MOED feels confident in its ability to meet these goals.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2526, 395, 2026, 8604, NULL, 8604, NULL, 8604, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8000, 'The number of slots available for YouthWorks participants is based on the amount of funding from a variety of sources, including the Baltimore City general funds, to pay the salaries of the youth. MOED will continue to collaborate with funders, recognizing that private funding is not guaranteed and that fundraising efforts must be balanced with MOED’s numerous strategic priorities.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2527, 396, 2026, 0.95, NULL, 0.95, NULL, 0.95, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Staff will increase outreach efforts to employers to improve survey participation, including training sessions scheduled to coordinate with employer availability and the availability of staff to provide support and troubleshooting throughout the summer. Numeric values based on historic data', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2528, 397, 2026, 0.87, NULL, 0.87, NULL, 0.87, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The survey questions include a scale of scoring that asks if the young person feels like their skills have increased over their time in the program in categories like time management, career exposure, financial literacy, and was the worksite engaging for the youth.  Numeric values based on historic data', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2529, 398, 2026, 62, NULL, 159, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 239, 'The number of participants serviced is based on the responses from providers from an RFP outlining the number of proposed youth to be served and the service delivery model based on Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act requirements. The local labor market analysis of high-wage/high growth areas is the driving force of the target areas for occupational training. There are specific occupational training areas sought for the youth population in which MOED provides the oversight.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2530, 399, 2026, 0, NULL, 0.13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.67, 'These Federal Funds are disbursed from the U.S. Department of Labor and passed through the MD Department of Labor and the performance measure definitions are outlined in the legislation. The percentage of those achieving measurable skills gains and credentials targets are set based on the WIOA performance negotiations conducted between MOED and the MD State Department of Labor following the WIOA guidelines. MOED is subjected to multiple monitorings by MD DOL through each program year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2531, 400, 2026, 0, NULL, 0.44, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.58, 'These Federal Funds are disbursed from the U.S. Department of Labor and passed through the MD Department of Labor and the performance measure definitions are outlined in the legislation. The percentage of those achieving measurable skills gains and credentials targets are set based on the WIOA performance negotiations conducted between MOED and the MD State Department of Labor following the WIOA guidelines. MOED is subjected to multiple monitorings by MD DOL through each program year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2532, 401, 2026, 3, NULL, 2, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4, 'The target for community engagement remains set at four events during the fiscal year. This goal reflects our ongoing commitment to building and strengthening partnerships, with a particular focus on engaging with youth. By concentrating our efforts on creating meaningful connections with younger community members, we aim to foster a sense of empowerment and awareness about the resources and opportunities available through the Wage Commission. Additionally, we seek to expand our network of partnerships to enhance our outreach and impact, ensuring that our initiatives are inclusive and responsive to the diverse needs of the community. Through these efforts, we strive to create a more informed and engaged community that is better equipped to access and benefit from our services.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2533, 402, 2026, 96, NULL, 110, NULL, 46, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 180, 'For FY26, our goal is to issue 180 late payroll violations or fewer. To achieve this, we will focus our efforts on strengthening collaboration with contracting agencies and those responsible for compliance. Our aim is to create a proactive approach that begins at the earliest stages of the process, starting with the inspection of bid documents. By ensuring that all contractors are fully aware of the city’s payroll mandates and compliance requirements upfront, we can work to minimize delays and improve adherence to established guidelines. This forward-focused strategy will allow us to address potential issues before they arise, fostering a higher level of compliance and reducing the need for enforcement actions.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2534, 403, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 0.95, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'Our target for fiscal year collections is set at 85%, which is designed to accommodate and anticipate potential issues such as litigation delays and other unforeseen challenges. This target reflects a realistic approach, considering the complexities that can arise during case resolutions. Additionally, it takes into account the legal authority granted to board members to reduce fines under certain circumstances. This ability to adjust fines ensures flexibility in our approach, allowing us to achieve fair and equitable outcomes while still striving to meet our overall collection goals. By setting our target at 85%, we maintain a balance between ambition and practicality, ensuring that we can effectively manage and resolve cases while adapting to any challenges that may arise.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2535, 404, 2026, 0.81, NULL, 0.91, NULL, 0.97, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The target for fiscal year 2026 remains unchanged, as it reflects our commitment to accommodating all influencing factors and anticipating ongoing changes. We recognize the complexities involved in the case closure process, including the need for thorough documentation review, varying levels of cooperation from contracting agencies, and potential delays due to contractor requests and external factors. By maintaining our current target, we aim to provide a realistic and achievable timeline that accounts for these variables while still striving for efficiency and fairness. This approach allows us to remain adaptable to continuous changes and challenges, ensuring that we can effectively manage each case with the necessary attention and diligence.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2536, 405, 2026, 8, NULL, 16, NULL, 158, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 50, 'The Fiscal Year 2026 target was established based on the filling of the previously vacant Legislative Liaison role and the overall improvement in capacity for the service in Fiscal Year 2025.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2537, 406, 2026, 16, NULL, 24, NULL, 12, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 14, 'The actual data from FY 24 and the statutory requirements were considered in establishing the FY26 target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2538, 407, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The target for Fiscal 2026 was established based on the success of the previous fiscal years data.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2539, 408, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The Fiscal 2026 target was established based on the previous fiscal years performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2540, 409, 2026, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4, 'The Fiscal Year 2026 target was established based on Fiscal Year 2025. The set amount is what is within the capabilities of the staff to conduct investigations and studies to hold public hearings for the purpose of determining the existence of problems, practices, or conditions in the areas placed under its jurisdiction by this or any other ordinance or by State or Federal law.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2541, 410, 2026, 13, NULL, 6, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 35, 'Based on the 2024 actual data as well as the continued budget cuts by the EEOC and staffing shortages determined the target for 2026', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2542, 411, 2026, 0.2, NULL, 0.1, NULL, 0.1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'This target was established based on the data of 2024.  The investigators for the Community Relations Commission will continue to follow the best practices for investigations by using deadlines, benchmarks and targets', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2543, 412, 2026, 17, NULL, 20, NULL, 28, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 50, 'Increased staffing and scheduled board meetings allowed for more organized and efficient community outreach, resulting in a higher number of events being scheduled and attended.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2544, 413, 2026, 0.99, NULL, 0.99, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The Maryland Police Accountability Act of 2021 requires timely adjudication of misconduct investigations by either asking for additional information or making the determination to charge the officer with misconduct.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2545, 414, 2026, 0.93, NULL, 0.99, NULL, 0.94, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The Maryland Police Accountability Act of 2021 requires timely complaint delivery to the law enforcement agency and the Police Accountability Boards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2546, 415, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'Continuation of prior year goals.  With a now fully-staffed Design Team, we are better able to provide design services that will help improve development in our City, support master planning activities, and improve the design environment.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2547, 416, 2026, 0.789, NULL, 0.889, NULL, 0.45, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'Continuation of prior year goals.  A new hire was brought aboard to replace the retiree early in FY25, so service should continue as expected.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2548, 417, 2026, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'Continuation of prior goals.  A new hire was brought aboard to replace the lost staffer, so service should continue as expected.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
