    (2573, 443, 2026, 0.93, NULL, 0.77, NULL, 0.58, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Focus deterrence policing cannot be pre-planned with specific percentages, as its effectiveness and implementation vary on a case-by-case basis. The approach is highly dependent on the number of group members involved in any given incident, the nature of the crime, and the local context. Each situation requires a tailored strategy, considering factors such as group dynamics, historical crime patterns, and community engagement. Attempting to quantify its impact in advance with fixed percentages would overlook the complexities of real-world policing and the adaptability required for successful deterrence._x000D_
