    (2763, 38, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20, 'Target was established because 1 of 2 staff members has retired.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2764, 39, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.03, 'Short-term rates are expected to drop based on expectation of fed cuts.  3% is an achievable target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2765, 40, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'This measure should be removed because multiple-alarm fires are heavily influenced by external factors such as building conditions and weather. Additionally, improved training encourages earlier resource requests, which may increase alarms but reflects safer incident management, not larger fires.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2766, 41, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target was established to align with the current NFPA 1710 standard, ensuring the Department’s performance benchmarks reflect nationally recognized expectations for fire service response and operational readiness.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2767, 42, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'BCFD will always strive for a goal of zero fatal fires. To support this effort, the Department conducts Saturday Safety Sweeps and additional weekly safety initiatives focused on fire prevention, community education, and identifying hazards before incidents occur.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2768, 43, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 48000, 'The intended outcome is to increase the percentage of occupants/residents that are alerted to smoke or fire inside of a structure and make it out safely. Success is measured by the reduction in Civilian Injuries and Fire Fatalities inside of structures._x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2769, 44, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100, 'We expect to continue to see growth in the program. Interest in the training continues to grow and we plan to host more trainings with our Resiliency Hubs and promote with Faith-based partners. Therefore we raised our goal to 100 individuals trained per year which is achievable with our resources.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2770, 45, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12, 'With a dedicated T&E coordinator, OEM now captures data for training and exercises lead by OEM or other local/regional/state entities and ensures we have coverage. The coordinator is also able to help develop and lead more exercises. Therefore we raised our goal to reflect accordingly.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2771, 46, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 30, 'Moving forward, OEM will collect data based on the report completed by the Duty Officer after an on-scene response. This will ensure data accurately reflect the number of OEM responses. We expect the number to go down with this change to the data collection which is reflected in our target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2772, 47, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'OEM will continue to spend 100% of grant funds.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2773, 48, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 160000, 'The FY27 target of 160,000 EMS dispatches reflects historical demand, projected population growth, and call volume trends. The goal assumes stable staffing, continued funding for frontline resources, and optimized deployment and triage protocols to manage call flow efficiently.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2774, 49, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1200, 'The FY27 outreach target remains at 1,200 to align with sustainable staffing, funding, and program capacity. While the program has historically exceeded this level, the target reflects a realistic benchmark that maintains accountability while supporting consistent, high-quality outreach services.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2775, 50, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target aligns with the NFPA benchmark of 90% of EMS responses within 9 minutes. The goal assumes gradual improvement through continued hiring of EMTs and paramedics, expanded recruit classes, deployment adjustments based on call volume, and improved coordination with hospitals to reduce off', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2776, 51, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'we are requesting to remove', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2777, 52, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.35, 'The FY27 outreach target remains at 1,200 to align with staffing capacity, funding, and program sustainability. Although the program has exceeded this level previously, the target reflects a realistic benchmark that supports accountability and consistent community outreach.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2778, 53, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3000, 'The FY27 target accounts for the retirement of the officer currently leading this program. Onboarding and acclimating a new officer may temporarily affect performance, particularly given the role’s dynamic nature and frequent interaction with the community.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2779, 54, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'This metric should be remove as of FY2024', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2780, 55, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5000, 'The FY27 target of 5,000 naloxone kits supports sustainable harm-reduction efforts. It assumes stable staffing trained in naloxone use, consistent funding for kit supply, and the ability to integrate distribution into routine EMS responses while accounting for call volume and supply constraints.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2781, 56, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'This metric should be remove as of FY2024', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2782, 57, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 500, 'The FY27 target reflects the anticipated retirement of the officer overseeing this program and the transition to the Department’s new website. The updated platform may temporarily affect how easily community members navigate and submit requests during the adjustment period.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2783, 58, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15000, 'The FY27 target was set based on sustained operational capacity and anticipated workload levels. BCFD will continue using strategic workload distribution, monthly performance tracking, and consistent supervisory oversight to maintain productivity and service delivery.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2784, 59, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2100, 'In FY27, we will continue monitoring caseload distribution and workload trends, particularly during periods of increased development activity, to ensure resources remain balanced and inspections are completed efficiently.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2785, 60, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2400, 'In CY25, BCFD also implemented a Third-Party Plans Review option. This provides customers with an additional pathway to move their projects forward by utilizing qualified external reviewers while maintaining departmental oversight.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2282, 81, 2026, 1088, NULL, 585, NULL, 820, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2500, 'Continued field training goals based on current projections on grant funding', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2787, 62, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Continued implementation of policies and procedures, along with daily monitoring of the 311 system, ensures complaints and fire code violations are addressed and resolved within the appropriate timeframe.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2788, 63, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'For FY27, the goal is to continue building on FY25 performance while maintaining recruitment efforts for additional plans reviewers. This role remains historically difficult to fill due to the specialized expertise required.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2789, 64, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 130, 'The FY27 target will remain the same, as weather conditions and related fire activity can vary year to year. Fire companies continue to mitigate risks by boarding vacant homes through TEZ sweeps and after dwelling fires to help prevent future incidents.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2790, 65, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 500, 'Policies are being reinforced to ensure on-scene company officers request fire investigations when appropriate, including for smaller trash fires. This helps ensure incidents are properly reviewed and supports consistent investigative practices.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2791, 66, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Staffing informed the FY27 target. BCFD piloted assigning a second investigator on select shifts, which has helped operations. Because this remains a pilot program, the BCFD maintained the existing target rather than increasing it.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2792, 67, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'The FY27 target will remain unchanged. With recent leadership changes in the Office of the Fire Marshal, maintaining the current benchmark allows performance to be monitored consistently and ensures timely corrective actions can be taken if needed.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2793, 68, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The FY27 target reflects the BCFD''s continued commitment to expanding training opportunities with partner agencies and external stakeholders. The goal assumes ongoing collaboration to ensure consistent interpretation of fire code requirements and unified safety standards.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2794, 69, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'Recent leadership changes have reinforced accountability and ensured members are meeting required training standards. Continued oversight and emphasis on professional development will help maintain compliance with investigative training requirements.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2795, 70, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'All in-service ground ladders are tested in accordance with NFPA 1932 to ensure firefighter and public safety. Ladders that fail inspection must be repaired or replaced before returning to service. Historically, about 20% fail annually, resulting in roughly $100,000 in replacement costs.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2796, 71, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'The Department maintains a 100% compliance target to ensure all members have safe, functional turnout gear. Annual NFPA 1851 inspections support firefighter safety, operational readiness, and help forecast gear replacement needs for effective budgeting and long-term planning.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2797, 72, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, 'Operative IQ provides a centralized platform for inventory, reporting, and tracking repairs, requests, and costs. The system improves accountability, reduces waste, supports timely repairs, and strengthens NFPA compliance while helping maintain the Department’s ISO Class 1 rating.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2798, 73, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 168000, 'The FY27 target reflects recent EMS call trends and projected community demand. The goal assumes stable staffing levels and consistent unit availability to ensure the Department can maintain reliable EMS response across the city.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2799, 74, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 52000, 'The FY27 target was set based on recent call volume trends and projected service demand. It assumes stable staffing levels and consistent unit availability to ensure the Department can meet operational needs and maintain reliable emergency response coverage.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2800, 75, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.98, 'The FY27 target builds on the strong FY25 performance of 98%. It assumes continued QA monitoring, ongoing training, and stable staffing levels, while maintaining high performance standards and accounting for potential changes in call volume and operational demands.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2801, 76, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target is based on recent performance trends of 89–92% and reflects a modest, achievable improvement. It assumes improved staffing stability as new hires complete training, continued CAD workflow optimization, and focused QA efforts to strengthen call processing efficiency.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2802, 77, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target builds on recent 90% performance and expected call demand. It assumes improved staffing, better peak-hour scheduling, and continued monitoring of ECats data to support steady improvement while recognizing ongoing staffing constraints.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2803, 78, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.96, 'The FY27 target was set using prior high performance levels (97–99%) as a benchmark. The goal assumes improved staffing stability, continued QA coaching, refresher protocol training, and consistent policy application to support a return toward historical performance levels.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2804, 79, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 18, 'The continued downward trend in line-of-duty injuries allowed the Department to adjust the FY27 target to reflect improved safety outcomes and ongoing progress in injury prevention.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2805, 80, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100, 'As vacancy rates stabilize the FY target is a realistic goal for ongoing hiring numbers taking historical attrition rates, minimum staffing and retirement eligibility into account._x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2806, 81, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2500, 'The FY27 target reflects successful grant funding that supports overtime for instructors and participating students. These resources expand training capacity and ensure programs can be delivered consistently without impacting daily operational staffing._x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2807, 82, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 325, 'The FY27 target reflects a realistic projection based on recent upward performance trends and anticipated operational demand.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2808, 83, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'The target reflects a realistic performance level based on the course curriculum, training requirements, and recognized industry standards for recruit completion and certification.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2809, 85, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.05, 'This number has been consistently between 5% and 3% for several fiscal years. Fleet doesn''t expect to see any large movement from that range in FY27.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2810, 86, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'This target is ambitious and Fleet needs to perform optimally in order to achieve it (in terms of repairs, vehicle replacement, staff retention, etc). Fleet is at about 83.3% for FY26 to date, which is close enough to 85% that it seems within reach.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2811, 87, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'This target is ambitious and Fleet needs to perform optimally in order to achieve it (in terms of repairs, vehicle replacement, staff retention, etc). Fleet is at about 77% for FY26 to date, which meets this target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2812, 89, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 60, 'Energy data is three months in arrears due to the timing of issued bills and corrections, so data will be available three months after FY close. The target is set based on the median average across the country from DoE report for the average office building.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2813, 90, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1500000, 'Targets based on available grants, award likelihood, and funding climate', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2814, 92, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.44, 'This is the Renewable Portfolio Standard''s percentage. Until FY27, the city''s targets were grandfathered in under previous legislation capped at 20%. This was because the city''s electric contract was put in place before changes to the statewide RPS.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2815, 93, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'The FY27 target of 70% was established using the historical average of 40% as a baseline and then intentionally set higher to reflect planned operational improvements tied to the JLL assessment, ongoing recruitment, contract renewals, and the development of SOPs and staff training.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2816, 94, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Elevator availability has remained relatively the same, with historical averages above 90%. Similar to grass mowing, the FY27 target adopts the prior year target. Elevator availability is influenced by asset age, parts availability, and vendor response.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2817, 96, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'We took into consideration our new industry standard SLAs as applied to our historical data and our new operational changes (changing of work windows from 21 to 60 days), leading to what we believe is a reachable target of 80%.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2818, 97, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The target for FY27 is based on the average percentage across FY15-FY25', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2819, 98, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.74, 'The target for FY27 is based on the average percentage across FY15-FY25', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2820, 99, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'We will maintain 90% of target for FY27 as we are building sufficient historical data', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2821, 100, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'We will maintain 90% of target for FY27 as we are building sufficient historical data', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2822, 102, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The target for FY27 is based on the average percentage across FY15-FY25', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2823, 103, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2824, 104, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1100, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2825, 105, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2826, 106, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2827, 107, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2828, 108, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 500, 'Based off of previous years, Childhood Lead Poisoning Prevention believes that the goal of 500 is attainable, via increased positions filled, outreach, education, partnerships and increased point of care testing.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2829, 109, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2830, 110, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.95, 'The FY27 goals were established based on a realistic interpretation of the available data and the program’s current capacity. They reflect both the trends observed in prior years and the challenges that have affected program implementation. These goals are designed to be achievable.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2831, 111, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8000, 'In FY27 the program will add 2 additional trainers, thereby increasing overall capacity for conducting naloxone training.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2832, 112, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8500, 'BCHD is currently increasing program staffing. In FY27, the team will collaborate with other agencies/organizations to expand naloxone kit distribution. In addition, "Naloxboxes" will be installed in city buildings to provide free access to naloxone kits and increase distribution to city residents.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2833, 113, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000000, 'FY27 target (1,000,000 syringes exchanged) is an ~11% increase over FY25 actuals. We anticipate level funding for FY27, but still expect to hit the new target. We''ve increased staffing and will expand outreach to include both mobile and street-based engagement (backpacking and pop-up events).', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2834, 114, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 320, 'This performance metric will be maintained at the same level as FY26. Staffing vacancies impacted operations in FY25 and FY26; however, the program is currently expanding staffing with new hires. They will reach full operational capacity early in FY27 and expect no issues meeting the target metric.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2835, 115, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 525, 'The FY27 target will be the same as for FY26 as services are being maintained at the same level.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2836, 116, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target will remain at 90%. This figure also aligns with regional and state performance standards for 988 call centers.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2837, 117, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4400, 'In FY26, the MCH Bureau hired a new Director for ARH and moved from the 1515 North Avenue clinic to a more desireable location.  If the Title X funds for the ARH office are maintained, we believe we can increase the volume of clients served from FY25; however, the funding environment is very vulnera', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2838, 118, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 130, 'Nurse Family Partnership model element 12 a full-time nurse home visitor carries a caseload between 21 and 25 active clients.  This metric contains the average caseload at an agency, state, and national level.  We have 6 full-time nurses in which the combined caseloads would be anywhere between 126-', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2839, 119, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.95, 'The FY27 target of 90% (a high bar given that many Baltimore City families are highly mobile and have significant competing prioties leading to missed visits and lower program retention compared with national averages) was retained and presumed continued strong retention of the nurse home visitors.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2840, 120, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 300000, 'It is expected that the target for FY2026 will be met or exceeded. It is anticipated that this trend will continue. As such the target for FY2027 represents a 1.5% increase over the FY2026 target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2841, 121, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'It is anticipated that there will be a significant increase in the actual performance in FY2026 due to increased staffing. Providing staffing remains stable, that trend is expected to continue through FY2027.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2842, 122, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.87, 'The return to class rate of 87% in FY2024 and FY2025 is the highest it has been in recent years.  Students will continue to sustain acute injuries and seasonal or communicable respiratory illnesses, and should be sent home. As such the return to class rate is not expected to significantly increase.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2843, 123, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2700, 'FY27 target was established using historical program performance data, referred clients, and staffing capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2844, 124, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1800, 'FY27 target was established using historical program performance data, referred clients, level of client need, and staffing capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2845, 125, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 'FY27 target was established using historical program performance data, waiver referrals, level of client need, and staffing capacity.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2846, 126, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 75, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2847, 127, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2848, 128, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 650, 'FY27 target is based on continuation of training with BCFD''s staff. With roughly 1678 employees, in cohorts of up to 18 per week, the program projected that at least  40% of the total staff will be reached additionally during this period.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2849, 129, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 600, 'The FY27 target was based on actual numbers for FY26 YTD.  The program increases its outreach efforts in September in observance of Suicide Prevention Awareness Month. We will continue this strategy in FY27, adding Mental Health Awareness month, to duplicate outreach efforts to meet annual target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2850, 131, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'Despite fluctuations in response and satisfaction rates following our trainings for BCFD on a monthly basis, the program continues to maintain its confidence in the satisfaction category in the 90 percentile, with a possible standard deviation of +/- 5%.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2851, 132, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The program will continue training BCFD in 2027 until all staff have been trained.  To maintain these consistent standards of the program''s training, it was necessary to set a goal that continues to promote high quality training across diverse groups despite subtle differences among trainees.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2852, 133, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10000, 'The shelter strives to lower the number of animals entering the shelter by providing resources to families to keep their pets. If programs to assist owners are properly funded then the target of 10,000 or below is achievable.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2853, 134, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Animal Control believes that with appropriate staffing and training, 100% closure rate is feasible.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2854, 135, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The national goal for a shelter''s live release rate is 90%.  If properly funded, the shelter would be able to meet this necessary target.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2855, 136, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4500, 'The target is set at 4500 inspections.  As this measure has only been tracked for the last 3 fiscal years our program believes that with the appropriate resources and staffing we can achieve the total number of inspections.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2856, 137, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'The target is set to 100% because our program believes that with the appropriate resources, all calls can be resolved within the expected timeframe.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2857, 138, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The target is set to 5 because our program believes that there may be an increase in new food establishments as the economy recovers.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
    (2858, 139, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1000, 'The FY27 target is based on the number of licensed tobacco retailers. We are required to conduct at least one compliance check for each retailer each year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
