    (2877, 159, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4500, 'The rehab programs have been converted from forgivable loan to grants, removing constraints on use of funds. We expect housing counseling and led remediation to remain on trend. Additionally, we have increased compliance requirements for quarterly reporting that allows for more accurate actuals info', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
