    (2928, 216, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 250, 'As the Defensive Litigation team has limited control over the amount and type of civil claims that will be filed, the FY27 target was established by reviewing previous years data (average over the last 3 fiscal years) and trends in current infrastructure, policy and legal changes.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486', '2026-06-26T16:54:00.999486'),
