    (3015, 360, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 188, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3016, 361, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5000, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3017, 362, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.95, 'As a result of anticipated reduction in federal funding and/or more restrictive requirements for the clients we serve, our targeted measures remains the same as FY25.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3018, 363, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.07, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3019, 364, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.3, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3020, 365, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.14, NULL, 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3021, 366, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'This metric is just for us to report out. We cannot estimate how many people will need to use interpreters.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3022, 367, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.75, 'Because of the high issuance, we are facing a large backlog. There''s also the difficulty getting/retaining a Scheduler. I believed that the FY26 numbers would be great but that was based on DHCD''s prior rate of issuance & a Scheduler coming on board. Considering our YTD, FY27 will be a challenge.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3023, 368, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'I kept the target at 90% because we''re seeing more citations (again, higher issuance) and more opportunities for disagreement among the Board. FY26 has had the most contentious Board meetings with the Board questioning the language of the Code and whether situations were exacerbated by others.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3024, 369, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 13, 'I decided to hold at 13 days because  in FY26 there has been an increase in issuance (i.e.  increase in volume and  longer turnaround). Further, the hearing officer that routinely handles these requests is leaving. We will start FY27 with a new hearing officer doing these, which requires training.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3025, 370, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 14, 'I re-set us to our prior target. The issuance of citations in FY26 might be the highest in the past decade. This means that we will likely see a higher volume of requests in FY27. We were at 14 days in FY25, we will likely be similar this year and next.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3026, 371, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'All quarterly reports due to the U.S. Department of Treasury will be submitted on time.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3027, 372, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 641170126, 'The ARPA expenditure deadline is December 31, 2026, with all administrative funds requiring spend down by April 30, 2027. Therefore, all $641,170,126 in ARPA funds will be spent by the end of FY27. This measure is cumulative across all fiscal years.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3028, 373, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 30, 'All projects will end by December 31, 2026, with the majority of projects ending prior to FY27. Therefore, the number of performance meetings will signficantly reduce in FY27.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3029, 374, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'All grants providing assistance to small businesses will end prior to FY27, therefore no small businesses will be served by ARPA in FY27 prior to the ARPA expenditure deadline on December 31, 2026.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3030, 376, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 120, 'Target established based on contract with BCPS and their expectations for students who would need YO Academy services due to poor performance in traditional high school.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3031, 377, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'Career Coaches seek to reach all students; however, absences, especially from chronically absent students, most notably in high schools, preclude coaches from reaching every student. Factoring in those limitations, this felt like an aspirational, but attainable, benchmark.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3032, 378, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.25, 'AIB guidance has clarified plans requirements. With new guidance, it will only be possible for 6th and 7th graders to be on-track for plans in FY27. Each year after a higher grade will be added. however, we request to change goal to reflect language and scope of Career Coach work.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3033, 379, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'Target established based on contract with BCPS and their expectations for students participation in work experiences.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3034, 380, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1200, 'Performance is set in contracts with MD Department of Social Services, based on their expected client enrollment and capacity given amount of funds granted.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3035, 381, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.45, 'Performance is set in contracts with MD Department of Social Services, based on their expected performance and capacity given amount of funds granted. Goals have not been modified to reflect greater difficulty in reaching off-case clients.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3036, 382, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'Performance set in contracts with MD DSS, based on expected performance and capacity given the funds granted. We request replace this goal with other contractural goals, as it''s more reflective of our ability to reach clients a well after program exit, rather than actual employment retention.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3037, 383, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 343, 'With the loss of ARPA funding and in lieu of an enhancement, agency is anticipating reducing number of Community Job Hubs in operation. Goal is reduced to reflect 3/7 fewer CJH staff to perform work.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3038, 384, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1835, 'With the loss of ARPA funding and in lieu of an enhancement, agency is anticipating reducing number of Community Job Hubs in operation. Goal is reduced to reflect 3/7 fewer CJH staff to perform work.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3039, 385, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 450, 'With the loss of ARPA funding and in lieu of an enhancement, agency is anticipating reducing number of Community Job Hubs in operation. Goal is reduced to reflect 3/7 fewer CJH staff to perform work.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3040, 386, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20000, 'Target represents traditional walk-in client population, reverting to pre-COVID baselines.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3041, 387, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.62, 'Target is contracturally defined by the state of Maryland based on a regression analysis that controls for client barriers and statewide historical performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3042, 388, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.62, 'Target is contracturally defined by the state of Maryland based on a regression analysis that controls for client barriers and statewide historical performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3043, 389, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1800, 'Goal is set in contract with Maryland Department of Public Safety and Correctional Services based on their expected performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3044, 390, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 400, 'Goal is set in contract with Maryland Department of Public Safety and Correctional Services based on their expected performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3045, 391, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 608, 'Due to the closure of the HEBCAC in December, YO is operating with one of two centers at half capacity. Increasing capacity to prior levels will take time, with expectations that a Q2 phase in to full capacity in Q3/4 yielding a 13/16 output from prior goal. FY27 should see return to prior level.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3046, 392, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'YO does not expect any deviations in model that would influence share of individuals receiving job readiness supports. These supports should be provided for most participants with more than a one-off engagement with YO.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3047, 393, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.37, 'HEBCAC Closure required phase in to prior service delivery. Placement and training lag enrollment by one quarter, leading to a slightly reduced expectation of 11/16 performance compared to prior goals. Note, recommendation to deprecate goal for # instead of %.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3048, 394, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'YO expects programming to continue to support alternatives to criminal justice involvement at existing levels.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3049, 395, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8000, 'With the loss of ARPA funding, YouthWorks is setting goals to prior operating levels. Acheiving even this level will still require significant funding that is not yet guaranteed.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3050, 396, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'No major changes in the YouthWorks model are expected to influence this outcome.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3051, 397, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'No major changes in the YouthWorks model are expected to influence this outcome.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3052, 398, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 228, 'Funding for program is based on formulas that define need. Funds are then granted out to programs based on industry demand and past performance. These outcomes are contracturally negotiated with providers in their initial RFPs. RFPs for 2027 have not yet been issued, goal is based on FY26 contracts.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3053, 399, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.68, 'Target is contracturally defined by the state of Maryland based on a regression analysis that controls for client barriers and statewide historical performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3054, 400, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.58, 'Target is contracturally defined by the state of Maryland based on a regression analysis that controls for client barriers and statewide historical performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3055, 401, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 6, 'FY27 target is 6 to maintain the higher level of collaboration that supports compliance and case prevention. Regular forums/presentations strengthen partnerships, increase awareness of wage requirements, improve reporting, and reduce repeat issues across contracts.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3056, 402, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 180, 'FY27 target is set at 180 to reflect expected variation in contractor compliance. Late payroll violations depend on contractor practices and timely submissions, not investigator actions. The target assumes continued outreach, technical support, and steady enforcement follow-up.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3057, 403, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'FY27 target is set at 85% to reflect external constraints: untimely contractor responses, extension requests, and Board decision timelines. Restitution collection is also impacted when contractors ignore notices and the City lacks a clear process to collect unpaid restitutions.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3058, 404, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.85, 'The FY2027 target (85%) reflects external factors outside investigators’ control, including timely contractor responses, requests for extensions, and the timing of final case decisions by Board members.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3059, 405, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 62, 'The target was increased based on the legislative work conducted in the previous year, along with the addition of the Veterans Commission, which expanded the scope and reach of the service''s equity efforts.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3060, 406, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 42, 'The target was developed following a review of the prior year''s calendar and with consideration of the addition of the Veterans Commission, which informed a more comprehensive and realistic goal for the service.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3061, 407, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The target for Fiscal 2027 was based on the success of the previous fiscal year.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3062, 408, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 'The Fiscal year 2027 target was established based on the previous fiscal years performance.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3063, 409, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 4, 'The target for FY27 is still 4 because we are on track to meet this target for FY26.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3064, 410, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 40, 'This target is based on the previous iscal years data as well as training new investigators', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3065, 411, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.5, 'This target is established based on Fy 25', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3066, 412, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 60, 'The FY27 target builds on recent outreach activity and reflects a continued commitment to community engagement, public education, and collaboration with stakeholders.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3067, 413, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target reflects historical performance trends and supports timely case processing while allowing flexibility for case complexity and interagency coordination.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3068, 414, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.9, 'The FY27 target maintains a realistic benchmark based on prior performance trends while accounting for operational variation in case processing._x000D_
_x000D_', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3069, 415, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to the satisfactory performance by staff supporting UDAAP and no expected changes in operating budget support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3070, 416, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to the satisfactory performance by the BMZA liaison and no expected changes in operating budget support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3071, 417, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.8, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to the satisfactory performance by Subdivision Program staff and no expected changes in operating budget support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3072, 418, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.7, 'Despite improved performance in FY2025 and FY2026 exceeding the existing target, the FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to caution about continued challenges with the Accela application.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3073, 419, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.6, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to no expected changes in operating budget support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3074, 420, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 70, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year due to no expected changes in operating budget support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3075, 422, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.55, 'The FY2027 target maintains the level from the prior fiscal year (after reducing the target for the past two years). Reports for the first two quarters of FY2026 exceeded the target but staff recommended keeping the existing target due to caution about challenges with the Accela application.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3076, 423, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 42000, 'The FY2027 target is a significant reduction from FY2026 (42K down from 85K) due to a proposed change in methodology to exclude web traffic to the Sustainability website. The target is based on the number of people engaged through events, the office newsletter, and other staff supported activities.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3077, 424, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 140, 'Agency staff expect staff engagement may increase with the addition of a new Waste Reduction training for DPW staff and other programs. However, to avoid the potential risk of overcounting staff engaged through multiple events, agency staff opted to keep the target at the same level as FY2026.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3078, 425, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.05, 'The FY2027 target is set at the same level as FY2025 and FY2026 based on the expectation of continued progress and no major change in operating funding for implementation support.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3079, 426, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.1, 'The FY2027 target is set at the same level as FY2025 and FY2026 based an expectation of continuous progress over the anticipated 10-year implementation period for the CAP Plan.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
    (3080, 427, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 170217, 'The FY2027 target is based on the proposed FY2027 budget for the Healthy Food Priority Area program funding with the assumption that all program funds will be granted to community organizations and urban farms.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
