    (3083, 430, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.4, 'BPD Patrol Bureau is currently (FY26 Q2) at a rate of 54% regarding time spent in proactive measures. While this figure exceeds the FY27 goal mark, the goal needs to be sustainable with increased summer CFS volume that will take away from availble time to engage in proactive measures.', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
