    (3087, 434, 2027, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.35, 'Even though we offer 6 CIT classes, as the # of trainees increase the % of CIT in patrol goes down. Until BPD makes the training required, CIT #s in patrol will be in flux due to new hires, retirements, and  movements within patrol and to other non patrol units', 2, '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508', '2026-06-26T16:54:01.000508'),
